NK097(je)001:8479: pa'i chos thams cad byed par 'gyur bas 'khor 'das
NK097(je)001:8480: kyi chos rnams kun gyi snying po'i rang bzhin du
NK097(je)001:8481: gyur pa'i don gang zhig /gdod nas skye ba med
NK097(je)001:8482: pa blo 'das rang byung gi ye shes yin pas
NK097(je)001:8483: rag pa'i gzhi dang phra ba'i rtsa ba kun las
NK097(je)001:8484: 'das pa'i snying po byang chub kyi sems 'di nyid
NK097(je)001:8485: / theg pa 'og ma'i rtog dpyod dang zhen 'dzin
NK097(je)001:8486: kun dang bral ba'i gnas lugs ji bzhin pa rtogs
NK097(je)001:8487: par byed pa'i rgyu ye grol bya rtsol dang bral
NK097(je)001:8488: ba'i dgongs pa mngon du phyung ba'i mdo lung zab
NK097(je)001:8489: mo 'di ni yang rab a ti'i skal ba dang
NK097(je)001:8490: ldan pa'i rjes 'jug rnams la gang zhig gdams par
NK097(je)001:8491: bya ba'i chos yin no zhes gdams bya'i chos ngos
NK097(je)001:8492: / bzung ba'o // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK097(je)001:8493: skal ldan byang chub snying po'i snod //
NK097(je)001:8494: skal med blo ngan dam nyams kyi snod bstan pa'o //
NK097(je)001:8496: thun mong dang thun mong ma yin pa'i yon tan gnyis dang ldan pa la sbyin par bstan pa /
NK097(je)001:8497: des kyang bla ma'i bka' bzhin dam bca' la gnas na sbyin pa /
NK097(je)001:8498: khyad par 'tsho yi bar du bka' bzhin sgrub pa'i
NK097(je)001:8499: mna' bskyal dus mdo lung yongs su rdzogs par sbyin
NK097(je)001:8500: pa / gtong phod che ba snod ldan gyi yo
NK097(je)001:8501: byad slob ma'i tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i don du blang
NK097(je)001:8502: pa / bar bstan pa'o // dang po ni /
NK097(je)001:8503: gong du bstan pa de lta bu'i man ngag khyad
NK097(je)001:8504: par can 'di gang la bstan pa'i yul ni gang
NK097(je)001:8505: zhe na / 'di ltar chos dang bla ma la
NK097(je)001:8506: zol zog med par yid ches mi 'gyur ba'i dad
NK097(je)001:8508: dam tshig srog dang bsdo zhing mi nyams par bsrung
NK097(je)001:8509: bas nyes ltung gi skyon gyis ma gos pa dang
NK097(je)001:8510: / gus rtag gi brtson 'grusa che bas zab mo'i
NK097(je)001:8511: nyams len la gcig tu gzhol ba'i sgom sran che
NK097(je)001:8512: / ba dang / 'gro kun pha mar shes pas
NK097(je)001:8513: brtse ba'i snying rje dang ldan zhing phrag dog dang
NK097(je)001:8514: 'gran sems med pas gzhan gyi yon tan la dga'
NK097(je)001:8515: ba'i yi rang dang ldan pa dang /
NK097(je)001:8516: dka' spyad drag po ji lta bu'i kyang lus sems skyo ba med pa dang /
NK097(je)001:8517: chos dang bla ma las yid phyir ldog pa med pa dang /
NK097(je)001:8518: 'dzin chags chung zhing gtong sems dang ldan pas rang
NK097(je)001:8519: gi lus dang gces pa'i bu dang mdza' ba'i chung
NK097(je)001:8520: ma dang nyan pa'i bran dang bsags pa'i nor sogs
NK097(je)001:8521: gang la'ang ma chagsa par bla ma la dad pa
NK097(je)001:8522: dang dga' bas 'bul bar nus pa sogs theg pa
NK097(je)001:8523: thun mong gi yon tan 'di dag mnga' ba ni
NK097(je)001:8524: dad pa dang dam tshig ldan pa'i rtags yin pas
NK097(je)001:8525: / de la snying po'i don dang ldan pa'i mtshungs
NK097(je)001:8526: med dpal mgon bla ma dam pas zab mo'i man
NK097(je)001:8527: ngag 'di nyid tshul bzhin du sbyin par bya'o //
NK097(je)001:8528: de bzhin du snyan dang gragsa pa la sogs pa chos brgyad kyi bsam pa spang zhing /
NK097(je)001:8529: bla ma dang mched lcam sogs la nga rgyal gyi blo dang bral ba dang /
NK097(je)001:8530: dam pa bla ma dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang man
NK097(je)001:8531: ngag snying po'i don gyi phyir du rang gi lus
NK097(je)001:8532: srog phongs pa med par gtong nus pa dang /
NK097(je)001:8533: bla mas ci gsung gi bka' las mi 'da' ba
NK097(je)001:8534: ste zab don snying po ji bzhin nyams su len
NK097(je)001:8535: par nus pa'i yon tan gyi rtags 'di dag dang
NK097(je)001:8536: ldan pa la chos thams cad kyi snying po sems
NK097(je)001:8537: nyid rang byung gi ye shes kyi don gab sbas
NK097(je)001:8538: med par rjen cer du ston zhing ngo sprad pa
NK097(je)001:8539: dang / chos thams cad kun skye med byang chub
NK097(je)001:8540: sems kyi rang bzhin rtsol med ye sangs rgyas pa'i
NK097(je)001:8541: rang bzhin du bstan pa yi rgyud don zab mo
NK097(je)001:8542: 'di nyid sbyin par bya'o zhes pa ste /
NK097(je)001:8544: dad pa'i stobs dang brtson 'grus che //
NK097(je)001:8545: shes rab che zhing 'dzin chags med //
NK097(je)001:8546: phu dud che zhing gsang sngags spyod //
NK097(je)001:8547: rtogs med sems la g.yengs ba med //
NK097(je)001:8548: dam tshig ldan zhing sgrub la brtson //
NK097(je)001:8549: breng nge dung nge brtse gdung ldan //
NK097(je)001:8550: lhang nge lhan ne sgom la spyod //
NK097(je)001:8551: slob dpon gsung pa ji bzhin spyod //
NK097(je)001:8552: dam tshig 'chal bar mi gtong zhing //
NK097(je)001:8553: spyod lam gzhan dang mthun par spyod //
NK097(je)001:8554: gus pa'i tshul gyi sems dngas shing //
NK097(je)001:8555: tshig gcig bstan pas rjes su 'dzin //
NK097(je)001:8556: rang gi don la de bzhin spyod //
NK097(je)001:8557: gsang ba gnyer gtad thub par byed //
NK097(je)001:8558: rdo rje'i don las mi 'da' zhing //
NK097(je)001:8559: thos pa che ba'i gang zag brten //
NK097(je)001:8560: rang gi don las 'da' ba med //
NK097(je)001:8561: dreg pa'i tshig med 'jam por smra //
NK097(je)001:8562: pha rol sems dang mthun 'jug byed //
NK097(je)001:8563: slob dpon dang ni de bzhin gshegs //
NK097(je)001:8564: khyad med gcig gi tshul du byed //
NK097(je)001:8565: de ni slob ma'i mtshan nyid do //
NK097(je)001:8566: de ltar ldan pa'i slob ma ni /
NK097(je)001:8567: rdzogs pa chen po'i snod du gsungs //
NK097(je)001:8568: zhes pa la sogs pa mdo rgyud rnams nas ji
NK097(je)001:8569: ltar bstan pa'i mtshan nyid dang ldan pa las gzhan
NK097(je)001:8570: du bstan na chos dang bla ma'i sku dgrar 'gyur
NK097(je)001:8571: zhing gdul bya'i rgyud kyang chud zos su 'gyur ba'o
NK097(je)001:8573: de lta bu'i skal ldan gyi gang zag khyad par
NK097(je)001:8574: can gang gis theg pa'i rtse rgyal snying po'i bstan
NK097(je)001:8575: pa 'di nyid bdag gis thos par gyur na /
NK097(je)001:8576: 'jig rten 'khor ba'i chos la mtshan mas te mtshan
NK097(je)001:8577: mar zhen cing don med pa'i dgag sgrub sna tshogs
NK097(je)001:8578: pa'i ngal ba byed pas bdag la cig bgyi ste
NK097(je)001:8580: des na shin tu thob par dka' ba mchog tu gsang ba'i man ngag 'di nyid thob na /
NK097(je)001:8581: bdag gis lus dang srog la mi lta bar dka'
NK097(je)001:8582: ba rgya chen po'i sgo nas tshul bzhin du sgrub
NK097(je)001:8583: bo zhes dam bca' 'dor ba med pa la legs
NK097(je)001:8584: par gnas na de la bstan pa'i snying po man
NK097(je)001:8585: ngag rdzogs pa chen po 'di nyid sbyin par gsungs
NK097(je)001:8586: pa ste / dper na lo chen bee ro tsa nas /
NK097(je)001:8587: rgyal bu g.yu sgra snying po la //
NK097(je)001:8588: rtsol med bde chen sangs rgyas thob 'dod na //
NK097(je)001:8589: khyod kyis nga la sbyangs pa dgu dang phod pa bcu gsum gyis shig gsungs pas /
NK097(je)001:8591: ma h+aa gu ru ci ltar gsungs pa bzhin nyan par bgyi /
NK097(je)001:8592: zhal nas bdud rtsi thig pa gnang bar zhu //
NK097(je)001:8593: zhes dam bca' phul ba bzhin no //
NK097(je)001:8594: de la sbyangs ba dgu ni /
NK097(je)001:8596: sbyang ba dgu ni 'di ltar gyis //
NK097(je)001:8597: bla ma'i yul zhing bzhugs gnas la //
NK097(je)001:8598: so nam las khur lus sems 'khor du gyis //
NK097(je)001:8599: de yis bskal par bsags pa'i sgrib pa sbyang //
NK097(je)001:8600: bla ma 'joms shing gnod pa'i sku dgra la //
NK097(je)001:8601: lus dang srog la mi lta bar //
NK097(je)001:8602: dgra choms dmag dang bsad bcad kyis //
NK097(je)001:8603: de yis bskal par bsags pa'i sgrib pa sbyang //
NK097(je)001:8604: bla ma'i zhabs tog don 'gyur na //
NK097(je)001:8605: sha rus khrag la 'bags la mnyes par bya //
NK097(je)001:8606: de yis bskal par bla ma'i sku dgrar gyur pa la //
NK097(je)001:8607: sad dang ser ba la sogs pa'i //
NK097(je)001:8608: drag sngags bzlas brjod tha dag bya //
NK097(je)001:8609: de yis bskal par bla ma'i sku dgrar gyur pa la //
NK097(je)001:8610: rdzun dang tshig barlanga shes cog smra //
NK097(je)001:8611: drag po'i shang chen sna tshogs gdab //
NK097(je)001:8612: de yi bskal pa bla ma'i skyon nas mi brjod par //
NK097(je)001:8613: yon tan sna tshogs brjod par bya //
NK097(je)001:8615: rtag tu spyi bo'i gtsug tu bla ma bkur //
NK097(je)001:8616: de yis bskal par rtag tu rtog tshogs yi dam lta //
NK097(je)001:8617: bsgom yang lha yi spyi gtsug bla ma bsgom //
NK097(je)001:8618: de yis bskal pa rtag tu mi brjed gdung ba'i sems kyis bla ma bkur //
NK097(je)001:8619: bla ma khog pa'i snying bzhin bkur //
NK097(je)001:8620: bla ma'i don du gyur pa na //
NK097(je)001:8621: bu dang chung ma yul 'khor dang //
NK097(je)001:8622: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK097(je)001:8623: rab tu gces pa'i nor rnams dang //
NK097(je)001:8625: de yis bskal par 'don klog sngags brjod ji snyed pa //
NK097(je)001:8626: bla ma'i sku dgrar gyur pa la //
NK097(je)001:8627: shes bcad rlang po'i tshig gcig dge //
NK097(je)001:8628: brgya phrag du ma'i char yang nyer mi phod //
NK097(je)001:8629: stong gsum 'jig rten mtha' dag tu //
NK097(je)001:8630: rin chen gser g.yu la sogs pa //
NK097(je)001:8631: rgyal ba'i sku gzugs sna tshogs bgyis //
NK097(je)001:8632: de la ji snyed bskor ba phyag 'tshal bas //
NK097(je)001:8633: bla ma mnyes pas 'gro don phrin las kyi //
NK097(je)001:8634: brgya phrag du ma'i char yang nyer mi phod //
NK097(je)001:8635: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten mtha' dag gis //
NK097(je)001:8636: nyan thos rang rgyal dge tshogs byas //
NK097(je)001:8637: byang chub sems dpa' mtha' dag la //
NK097(je)001:8638: ci snyed mnyes par byas pa bas //
NK097(je)001:8639: bla ma dar cig mnyes pa dge //
NK097(je)001:8640: brgya phrag du ma ci yi phyir zhe na //
NK097(je)001:8641: bskal pa 'bum gyi sangs rgyas pas //
NK097(je)001:8642: bla ma gnyan par shes par bya //
NK097(je)001:8643: des na sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa'i sku //
NK097(je)001:8644: dkon mchog gsum gyi rtsa ba ste //
NK097(je)001:8645: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK097(je)001:8646: rje bla ma rnams la skyabs su gsol //
NK097(je)001:8647: de ltar sbyangs pa dgu yis sbyongs shig /ces dang /
NK097(je)001:8649: lho nub o rgyan yul du song //
NK097(je)001:8650: kun bzang gdung tshob rgyal ba nyid dang mnyam //
NK097(je)001:8651: dga' rab rdo rje nyid la gser phye bre gang phul //
NK097(je)001:8652: dga' rab rdo rje'i gnang ba nga yis khyed la sbyin //
NK097(je)001:8653: 'jam dpal la sogs mkhas pa nyi shu rtsa gsum la //
NK097(je)001:8654: rin chen gser phye phul nas rkyang phyag stong du 'tshal //
NK097(je)001:8655: rgya gar mkhas pa'i 'dra 'bag nga yis khyed la sbyin //
NK097(je)001:8656: rdo rje gdan gyi sh+r+ai sing ha la //
NK097(je)001:8657: gser phye bre phyed phul la rkyang phyag stong du 'tshol //
NK097(je)001:8658: rgyud sde drug cu rtsa bzhi nga yis deng sang bod yul dbus kyi bsam yas na //
NK097(je)001:8659: rgyal po khri srong lde btsan gyis //
NK097(je)001:8660: mkhas pa bi ma mi tra spyan drangs nas //
NK097(je)001:8661: chos gra'i dpon slob de yis mdzad //
NK097(je)001:8662: mkhas pa mang po grwal ring bcug /skur pa chen po nga la 'debs //
NK097(je)001:8663: theg dman chos kyi 'khor lo bskor //
NK097(je)001:8664: g.yu sgra snying po der bzhud la //
NK097(je)001:8665: rgyal ba dgongs pa'i dge bsdur gyis //
NK097(je)001:8666: mkhas pa'i sgra bsgyur de ru 'gyur //
NK097(je)001:8667: rig pas sun phyung mthu dang rdzu 'phrul ston //
NK097(je)001:8668: bee ro tsa na nga yi rnam thar sgrogs //
NK097(je)001:8669: dbang dang gting rdzogs khyod la sbyin //
NK097(je)001:8670: bu dang chung ma khab tu zhog /lo dgu nga yi g.yog po gyis //
NK097(je)001:8671: man ngag rdzogs par khyod la sbyin //
NK097(je)001:8672: dbu skra gser g.yu'i lcang lo rtsad nas chod //
NK097(je)001:8673: gser dngul sor gdub rgyan cha phog /chur rtsar bcos pa'i ser gos gon //
NK097(je)001:8674: lo thug chan thug phye thug 'thung //
NK097(je)001:8675: rtag tu che dreg nga rgyal zhog /rgyal srid yul 'khor rgyab tu bskur //
NK097(je)001:8676: de tsho phod na man ngag bde chen rtsol med khyod la sbyin //
NK097(je)001:8679: khyad par ji srid du slob ma bdag rang dang
NK097(je)001:8680: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon 'tsho zhing bzhugs pa'i
NK097(je)001:8681: bar du de lus dang srog gi 'brel ba ma
NK097(je)001:8682: mchis par ma gyur gyi bar du /
NK097(je)001:8683: dpal mgon bla ma dam pa khyod kyi dka' spyad drag po ci lta bu gyis zhes gsungs kyang /
NK097(je)001:8684: sems la skyo ba dang lus la ngal ba med
NK097(je)001:8685: par bka'a bzhin dang du blang zhing sgrub par byed
NK097(je)001:8686: do ces bka' dam la gnas shing mna' bor ba
NK097(je)001:8687: la / bstan pa'i snying po kun byed rgyal po
NK097(je)001:8688: yi rgyud 'di yongs su rdzogs par sbyin par bya'o
NK097(je)001:8689: la / zhes so // bzhi pa ni /
NK097(je)001:8690: de ltar mdor na chos kyi yon du rang gi
NK097(je)001:8691: lus dang srog kyang 'phang ba med par dbul bar
NK097(je)001:8692: bya zhing gtong nus pa yin na /
NK097(je)001:8693: de las gzhan pa'i rdzas dang khang zhing yul 'khor
NK097(je)001:8694: rkang 'gros la sogs pa gtong bar byed nus pa
NK097(je)001:8695: smos ci dgos te de dag 'bul bar bya zhing
NK097(je)001:8696: / de yi tshe na bla mas kyang gal te
NK097(je)001:8697: bdag nyid la longs spyod de dag gis dgos pa
NK097(je)001:8698: gang yang yod par ma gyur kyang /
NK097(je)001:8699: slob ma'i tshogs rdzogs pa dang chos kyi che ba
NK097(je)001:8700: 'don pa'i phyir du bla ma dam pas blangs te
NK097(je)001:8701: dkon mchog gsum la 'bul bar bya dgos so //
NK097(je)001:8702: gnyis pa snod min la mi bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK097(je)001:8704: de la gsang bar gdams pa'o //
NK097(je)001:8706: kye sems dpa' rdo rje ston pa'i ston pa kun byed rgyal po nga yis /
NK097(je)001:8707: nges gsang snying po'i bstan pa sbyin pa'i snod min
NK097(je)001:8708: pa log pa'i lam la zhugs pa'i gang zag bstan
NK097(je)001:8709: pa ni / 'di ltar grags pa dang rnyed pa
NK097(je)001:8710: la sogs pa 'jig rten gyi chos la dga' zhing
NK097(je)001:8711: chags nas de'i dbang du song ba dang /
NK097(je)001:8712: rang rgyud nga rgyal gyis khengs pas chos dang bla
NK097(je)001:8713: ma la dam par mi bkur bar bla ma dang
NK097(je)001:8714: chos la smod cing mched la khro bar byed pa
NK097(je)001:8715: dang / yid dang rgyud thung pas bka' bkyon phra
NK097(je)001:8716: mo tsam gyis chos dang bla ma las blo sems
NK097(je)001:8718: 'phyar zhing g.yengs bas brtson 'grus lhod pa dang rdzas
NK097(je)001:8719: dang yo byad la chags shing ser sna che ba
NK097(je)001:8720: dang / bla ma dang mched la dad par mi ldan te /
NK097(je)001:8722: rang gi rgyud tshod la mi brtags shing dka' spyad
NK097(je)001:8723: brtson 'grus med par nyams len btsan thabs su skye
NK097(je)001:8724: bar 'dod pa yi lo 'dod che ba dang /
NK097(je)001:8725: rgyal ba'i bstan pa yongs la 'tshe zhing gnod pa 'phel zhing /
NK097(je)001:8726: chos dang bla ma mched grogs sogs la mi mthun
NK097(je)001:8727: pa'i bsam sbyor la zhugs nas smod par bya zhing
NK097(je)001:8729: rtag tu bdag dang gzhan gyi phyogs thams cad la
NK097(je)001:8730: gnod sems kyis rgyud 'khrugs shing snying po'i don la
NK097(je)001:8731: bsgom pa min pa de ni snod min dor bar
NK097(je)001:8732: bya ba'i mtshan nyid yin no //
NK097(je)001:8734: bshad ma thag pa de lta bu'i gang zag blo
NK097(je)001:8735: ngan log pa'i lam du zhugs pa 'di nyid la
NK097(je)001:8736: theg pa kun gyi yang rtse gsang chen a ti
NK097(je)001:8737: yo ga rtsol med rang byung gi theg pa 'di
NK097(je)001:8738: nyid mi bstan par ma zad rlung phyogs tsam yang
NK097(je)001:8739: mi bsgrags par mchog tu gsang bar bya'o zhes pa
NK097(je)001:8740: ste / gnas lugs rin po che'i mdzod las //
NK097(je)001:8741: bla ma smod cing mched la khro ba dang //
NK097(je)001:8742: gsang sgo 'chol zhing yongs la sgrogs pa dang //
NK097(je)001:8743: dad med ser sna che zhing ngang rgyud ngan //
NK097(je)001:8744: tshe 'di'i zhen pa can la gsang bar bya //
NK097(je)001:8746: gsum pa snod brtags pa la bzhi ste /
NK097(je)001:8748: snod ngan la mi sbyin pa /
NK097(je)001:8749: ma brtags par byin pa'i nyes pa mang bas skal chad la gsang ba /
NK097(je)001:8750: legs par brtags nas yo byad blang ste skal ldan
NK097(je)001:8751: la kun byed byang chub snying po'i rgyud bstan cing
NK097(je)001:8753: gong du bshad pa de lta bu'i snod dang ldan mi ldan sna tshogs yod pa'i phyir na /
NK097(je)001:8754: dang po gdams pa ma byin pa'i sngon du ji
NK097(je)001:8755: skad bshad pa'i rtags dang dad pa la sogs pa
NK097(je)001:8756: snod kyi mtshan nyid rnams yod dam med legs par
NK097(je)001:8757: brtags par bya ba'i phyir du /
NK097(je)001:8758: man ngag kun gyi snying po 'di nyid zhu ba'i
NK097(je)001:8759: yon du rin chen dbyig dang rkang 'gros bzhon pa
NK097(je)001:8760: chas gos longs spyod sna tshogs pa'i 'bul ba dang
NK097(je)001:8762: sgo gsum shin tu bsdam zhing gus pa dang ldan
NK097(je)001:8763: pas man ngag tshul bzhin tu ma nor bar byed
NK097(je)001:8764: pa'i gang zag de nyid kyi thob par bya ba
NK097(je)001:8765: las gzhan gang rung rung la sbyin par mi bya
NK097(je)001:8766: bar gsungs te / de nyid las /
NK097(je)001:8767: thos mang yon tan rdzogs pa'i bla mas kyang //
NK097(je)001:8768: snod bcud brtags te rim gyis gnad rnams byin //
NK097(je)001:8771: de la snying po'i man ngag mi sbyin pa'i snod ni gang zhe na /
NK097(je)001:8772: 'di ltar rdzas dang yo byad la chags sems dang ldan pas gtong mi bra ba dang /
NK097(je)001:8773: nga rgyal gyis rang rgyud khengs shing chos zab mo
NK097(je)001:8774: las gzhan 'jig rten tshe 'dis don la sems pa
NK097(je)001:8775: dang / blo gcig tu ma nges pas 'gyur ldog
NK097(je)001:8776: can gyi gang zag de ni snod ngan gyi rigs
NK097(je)001:8777: dang / yin la / des na de 'dra'i gang
NK097(je)001:8778: zag de la snying po byang chub sems kyi theg
NK097(je)001:8779: pa kun byed rgyal po 'di nyid bstan par mi
NK097(je)001:8780: dang / yin la / bya'o // tshul de ltar rtsal rdzogs las /
NK097(je)001:8781: gsang ba 'tshol bar byed ba yang //
NK097(je)001:8782: smra byed lce la zhing rmo zhing //
NK097(je)001:8783: sdug bsngal chen po myong bar 'gyur //
NK097(je)001:8784: de phyir nges pa'i don 'di gsang //
NK097(je)001:8787: de ltar snod kyi dbye ba dang de dag la
NK097(je)001:8788: snying po'i gdams pa bstan pa dang mi bstan pa'i
NK097(je)001:8789: khyad par gsungs pa de yang spyir chos nyid snying
NK097(je)001:8790: po'i don la snod du rung mi rung sogs bzang
NK097(je)001:8791: ngan blang dor gang yang mi gnas mod /
NK097(je)001:8792: 'on kyang gdul bya'i snang tshul la de 'dra'i khyad par yod pas /
NK097(je)001:8793: gal te de lta bu'i snod min la bstan na
NK097(je)001:8794: bdud dang gnod sbyin la sogs pa mi ma yin
NK097(je)001:8795: dang 'byung pos bla slob gnyis ka'i tshe srog la
NK097(je)001:8797: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro la sogs pa dam tshig
NK097(je)001:8798: gi so mtshams bsrung zhing sngags kyi dngos grub grub
NK097(je)001:8799: pa can kun gyis bla slob gnyis ka la dus
NK097(je)001:8800: min gyi 'chi ba gtong ba dang /
NK097(je)001:8801: nad gdon dgra bgegs la sogs pa 'jigs pa'i dbang du gyur nas tshe thung zhing /
NK097(je)001:8802: phyi mar yang ngan song du ltung ba dang /
NK097(je)001:8803: man ngag gi chos la sgro skur btab pa'i dbang
NK097(je)001:8804: gis snying po'i theg pa 'di nyid nub par 'gyur
NK097(je)001:8805: ba la sogs pa'i nyes pa shin tu mang ba
NK097(je)001:8806: de bas na / rigs ngan mtshan nyid dang mi ldan pa'i gang zag rnams spang bar bya'o //
NK097(je)001:8807: chos dbyings rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK097(je)001:8808: 'di ni mchog gsang theg pa'i yang rtse ste //
NK097(je)001:8809: blo dman rnams la mi smra shin tu gsang //
NK097(je)001:8810: sgro skur dbang gis snying po'i bstan pa 'chal //
NK097(je)001:8811: sgro 'dogs nyid dang dgongs pa log par zhugs //
NK097(je)001:8812: gsang sgo 'chol rnams mtha' med ngan 'gror ltung //
NK097(je)001:8815: de ltar slob ma'i rgyud brtags nas man ngag ston
NK097(je)001:8816: pa'i dus su skal ldan gyi slob ma de nyid
NK097(je)001:8817: 'jig rten gyi chos la zhen pa bral zhing /
NK097(je)001:8818: shes rgyud brtags pa'i phyir du lus dang longs spyod thams cad bla mas kun kyang blangs la /
NK097(je)001:8819: de ltar gtong nus pa dang mi nus pa'i khyad
NK097(je)001:8820: par gyi rtags dang ldan mi ldan rig par byas
NK097(je)001:8821: nas zhes / de ltar brtags pa'i tshul kyang /
NK097(je)001:8822: kun mkhyen gyis chos zhu ba'i sngon du snod dang ldan nam mi ldan brtags par bya ste /
NK097(je)001:8823: bya dka' ba'i las bcol ba'am /
NK097(je)001:8824: snying la phog pa'i tshig gis gshe ba'am /
NK097(je)001:8825: spyod lam 'gal 'dus mi dad pa brtags pa'am /
NK097(je)001:8826: nor 'di dang 'di 'dod ces gtong phod brtags pas /
NK097(je)001:8827: snod med yin na dad pa log pa'am yo byad la phongs pas phyir bzlos ste /
NK097(je)001:8828: de lta bu la ni phan thogs pa dang dam
NK097(je)001:8829: tshig thub pa mi srid pas ma 'brel ba legs
NK097(je)001:8831: zhes gsungs pa de lta bu'i tshul gyis brtags nas
NK097(je)001:8832: mtshan nyid dang ldan par rig na gzod man ngag
NK097(je)001:8833: snying po yi don bstan zhing theg pa'i yang rtse
NK097(je)001:8834: kun byed rgyal po mchog gi rgyud 'di sbyin par
NK097(je)001:8837: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po las bstan
NK097(je)001:8838: pa gang la bzhag pa'i le'u ste brgyad cu rtsa
NK097(je)001:8839: gsum pa'i 'grel pa'o ////gnyis pa mtshan gyi rnam grangs
NK097(je)001:8840: bstan pa'i le'u brgyad cu rtsa bzhi pa la gnyis
NK097(je)001:8844: de ltar man ngag zab mo'i rgyud 'di gang la
NK097(je)001:8845: gdams pa'i snod kyi khyad par bstan pa de nas
NK097(je)001:8846: byang chub kyi sems ston pa kun byed rgyal po
NK097(je)001:8847: la / rgyal sras sems dpa' rdo rjes spyod lam
NK097(je)001:8848: shin tu legs par gus shing 'dud pa'i tshul gyis
NK097(je)001:8849: zhal gyi gzi mdangs phyung ste ston pa kun byed
NK097(je)001:8850: nyid kyi mdun du 'khod nas gang zhig zhus pa
NK097(je)001:8851: la / yi don ni / kye rgyal ba sku
NK097(je)001:8852: gsum gyi ston pa'i ston pa kun byed rgyal po
NK097(je)001:8853: la / yi don ni / lags / nyid kyi
NK097(je)001:8854: thugs mtshan ma'i spros pa dang bral ba'i chos sku
NK097(je)001:8855: thig le nyag gcig rang byung ye shes chen po'i
NK097(je)001:8856: dgongs pa'i klong las shar ba'i rtsol med rang byung
NK097(je)001:8858: skal ldan gyi gang zag rnams dus gcig la grol
NK097(je)001:8859: bar mdzad pa'i mdo lung chen po 'di yi yon
NK097(je)001:8860: tan gyi che ba so so'i cha nas brjod pa'i
NK097(je)001:8861: mtshan gyi khyad par du zhig yod pa rnams bdag
NK097(je)001:8862: cag 'dus pa'i 'khor tshogs rnams la bshad par mdzad
NK097(je)001:8865: gang gsungs pa'i tshul mdor bstan pa dang /
NK097(je)001:8866: ji ltar gsungs pa'i don rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK097(je)001:8868: de ltar 'khor gyis zhus pa de nas ston pa
NK097(je)001:8869: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal pos theg pa
NK097(je)001:8870: thams cad kyi yang rtse rgyud kyi rgyal po chen
NK097(je)001:8871: po 'di nyid kyi mtshan gyi rnam grangs so sor
NK097(je)001:8872: rnam par phye ba yi sgo nas che ba'i yon
NK097(je)001:8873: tan bstan pa 'di nyid gsungs so //
NK097(je)001:8876: che ba'i yon tan brjod pa /
NK097(je)001:8877: de'i don 'dzin pa'i gang zag gis 'grub par bstan pa /
NK097(je)001:8878: kun las 'phags pa'i kun byed kun gyi snying po'i
NK097(je)001:8879: rgyud skal med la mi spel zhing skal ldan la
NK097(je)001:8880: snang ba'i don du sems dpa'i rdo rje la gtad
NK097(je)001:8881: pa'i tshul lo // dang po la bcu ste /
NK097(je)001:8882: lhun gyis grub pas kun byed rgyal por bstan pa /
NK097(je)001:8883: snying po rang bzhin dri ma med pas byang chub kyi sems su bstan pa /
NK097(je)001:8884: rgyu rkyen med par ye nas byung bas rang byung gi ye shes su bstan pa /
NK097(je)001:8885: chos rnams ji bzhin pa'i ngang du ston pa chos kyi me long du bstan pa /
NK097(je)001:8886: chos rnams gnyis su med pas snying po'i don gyi theg par bstan pa /
NK097(je)001:8887: dus gsum rgyal ba'i dgongs pa gzung 'dzin las 'das pa blta ba'i me long du bstan pa /
NK097(je)001:8888: smra bsam brjod du med pas rgyal ba'i yum du bstan pa /
NK097(je)001:8889: ma btsal lhun gyis grub par rgyud kyi rgyal por bstan pa /
NK097(je)001:8890: rnal bzhag sgro skur dang bral bas ma bcos don gyi lung du bstan pa /
NK097(je)001:8891: thams cad byang chub snying por ro gcig pas mdo don bsdus par bstan pa'o //
NK097(je)001:8893: kye sems dpa' rdo rje ston pa'i ston pa kun
NK097(je)001:8894: byed rgyal po nga yis yang rab a ti'i skal
NK097(je)001:8895: pa dang ldan pa'i gdul bya rnams la /
NK097(je)001:8896: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes ji bzhin pa
NK097(je)001:8897: ston par byed pa'i mdo lung chen po 'di yi
NK097(je)001:8898: mtshan gyi khyad par so sor phye ste bshad pa
NK097(je)001:8900: ji ltar snang ba'i 'khor 'das kyi chos 'di rnams
NK097(je)001:8901: thams cad kun gcig kyang ma lus par byed po
NK097(je)001:8902: gzhan med par / snying po rang byung gi ye
NK097(je)001:8903: shes kun byed byang chub kyi sems nyid kyis snga
NK097(je)001:8904: ma kun byas shing da lta ba byed cing ma
NK097(je)001:8905: 'ongs pa rnams byed par 'gyur ba yin te sngar
NK097(je)001:8906: gzhan med par / / byang chub sems ni kun byed rgyal po ste /
NK097(je)001:8907: dus gsum sangs rgyas byang chub sems kyis byas //
NK097(je)001:8908: khams gsum sems can byang chub sems kyis byas //
NK097(je)001:8909: snang srid snod bcud byang chub sems kyis byas //
NK097(je)001:8910: zhes gsungs pa ltar yin kyang /
NK097(je)001:8911: de lta bu'i chos rnams kyi kun gyi byed pa
NK097(je)001:8912: po sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes kun byed
NK097(je)001:8913: rgyal po rang nyid la rgyu rkyen gang gis kyang
NK097(je)001:8914: bskyed pa'i bya ba byed mi dgos te gdod nas
NK097(je)001:8915: skye ba med pa ye stong 'dus ma byas pa'i
NK097(je)001:8916: rang bzhin du lhun gyis grub pa yin pas na
NK097(je)001:8917: / de nyid brjod par byed pa'i rgyud 'di'i mtshan
NK097(je)001:8918: la kun byed rgyal po zhes su bstan pa yin
NK097(je)001:8920: de bzhin du kye sems nyid rang byung gi ye
NK097(je)001:8921: shes gang zhig chos thams cad gang las 'byung ba'i
NK097(je)001:8922: snying po nga la sgrib byed nyon shes kyi dri
NK097(je)001:8923: ma gdod nas med par dag pa nyag gcig tu
NK097(je)001:8925: sku dang ye shes yon tan thams cad ma btsal
NK097(je)001:8926: bzhin du nyi ma dang zer bzhin du rang chas
NK097(je)001:8927: lhun gyis grub pa'i tshul du rdzogs shing chub pa'i
NK097(je)001:8929: kun byed byang chub kyi sems 'di la da gzod
NK097(je)001:8930: dri ma sel ba dang yon tan rdzogs pa'i phyir
NK097(je)001:8931: du btsal zhing sgrub pa yi bya ba ci yang
NK097(je)001:8932: mi mnga' ba ste bsal bzhag thams cad dang bral
NK097(je)001:8933: ba yin pa'i rgyu mtshan des na de ltar ston
NK097(je)001:8934: pa'i theg pa 'di la snying po byang chub sems
NK097(je)001:8935: kyi theg pa zhes su nges par bstan pa yin
NK097(je)001:8937: kye ma 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad kyi
NK097(je)001:8938: 'byung gnas gdod nas ma btsal lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK097(je)001:8939: chos nyid rig pa byang chub kyi sems 'di la
NK097(je)001:8940: skye 'gag gi chos su grub pa med pas rgyu
NK097(je)001:8941: dang rkyen la ltos pa med cing /
NK097(je)001:8942: til la mar gyis khyab pa ltar sems can nas
NK097(je)001:8943: sangs rgyas kyi bar kun gyi sems kyi chos nyid
NK097(je)001:8944: rig pa rang gsal gyi ngo bo gnas pa yin
NK097(je)001:8945: pa dang / de las gzhan du 'bad rtsol gyis
NK097(je)001:8946: batsala du med pa'i rang bzhin mtha' bral nam mkha'
NK097(je)001:8947: lta bu'i snying po byang chub kyi sems 'di nyid
NK097(je)001:8948: gang gis kyang ma sgrib par 'khor 'das kun la
NK097(je)001:8949: phyogs dang ris su chad pa med par gsal zhing
NK097(je)001:8950: khyab pa yin pa'i rgyu mtshan de bas na /
NK097(je)001:8951: rgyu rkyen gyis 'dus ma byas par rang byung gi ye shes zhes su bstan pa yin te /
NK097(je)001:8953: rang byung ye shes 'char nub med //
NK097(je)001:8954: mtha' yi mun pa mi mnga' bas //
NK097(je)001:8955: phyi nang med par kun la gsal //
NK097(je)001:8958: kye dper na me long gi ngos la gzugs brnyan
NK097(je)001:8959: ji snyed snang ba thams cad me long gi nang
NK097(je)001:8960: du 'ub chub cing rdzogs pa dang /
NK097(je)001:8961: me long de nyid gzugs brnyan thams cad phyogs dang
NK097(je)001:8962: ris su chad pa med par kun gyi 'char gzhir
NK097(je)001:8964: ji ltar snang ba'i chos phyi nang 'khor 'das kyis
NK097(je)001:8965: bsdus pa 'di rnams thams cad kun sems nyid ma
NK097(je)001:8966: bcos ji bzhin pa'i ngang la med snang stong gzugs
NK097(je)001:8967: kyi rol pa tsam du chos kun snang ba yin
NK097(je)001:8968: pa'i rgyu mtshan de bas na /
NK097(je)001:8969: de ltar snang ba'i dus nyid nas rtag chad skye
NK097(je)001:8970: 'gag yod med 'gro 'ong la sogs pa gang gi
NK097(je)001:8971: yang phyogsa dang ris gnyis su chad pa'i don zhig
NK097(je)001:8972: grub pa med de zung 'jug mnyam gdal chen po
NK097(je)001:8973: spros bral blo las 'das pa yin zhing /
NK097(je)001:8974: de lta bu'i zung 'jug spros pa dang bral ba
NK097(je)001:8975: chos nyid mnyam pa chen po gnas lugs rang byung
NK097(je)001:8976: gi ye shes de ni dus gsum rgyal ba kun
NK097(je)001:8977: gyis ji snyed gsungs pa'i chos thams cad kyi dgongs
NK097(je)001:8978: pa'i zhe phug yin pa dang /
NK097(je)001:8979: rgyud 'di nyid kyis gnas lugs de gab sbas med par gsal bar ston pa yin pas /
NK097(je)001:8980: rgyud 'di'i mtshan la rgyal kun bka' yi dgongs pa
NK097(je)001:8981: mthar thug pa 'grel ba yi tshul gyis ston par
NK097(je)001:8982: byed cing theg pa thams cad kyi dgongs don gsal
NK097(je)001:8983: bar 'byed pas chos kyi me long zhes bstan pa
NK097(je)001:8984: yin te / theg pa'i spyi phud klong chen rab 'byams rgyal po las /
NK097(je)001:8985: theg pa ma lus kun 'byed pas //
NK097(je)001:8986: gsal bar byed pa'i me long yin //
NK097(je)001:8990: ji bzhin ma bcos pa yi gshis lugs sems nyid
NK097(je)001:8991: rang byung gi ye shes snying po rnal ma 'di
NK097(je)001:8992: la ma 'dus pa'i chos gcig kyang med pa'i phyir
NK097(je)001:8993: na / 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa
NK097(je)001:8994: yi chos thams cad tshur byung yang de las 'byung
NK097(je)001:8995: na / ba dang / phar sdud pa'am grol kyang
NK097(je)001:8996: de nyid kyi ngang du grol ba yin pas rig
NK097(je)001:8997: pa byang chub kyi sems 'di chos thams cad kyi
NK097(je)001:8999: de ltar chos nyid byang chub sems kyi klong nas
NK097(je)001:9000: 'khor 'das stong gzugs kyi rol pa sna tshogs su
NK097(je)001:9001: snang na yang / don la ka dag gzhi rtsa
NK097(je)001:9002: dang bral ba'i rang bzhin las 'khor 'das gang yang
NK097(je)001:9003: grub pa med pas theg pa 'og ma pa ltar
NK097(je)001:9004: spong 'gog sbyong bsgyur gyi rtsol ba gang yang mi
NK097(je)001:9005: snang na yang / dgos par / 'khor 'das blang
NK097(je)001:9006: dor du 'dzin cing chags pa'i rgya lasa rnam par
NK097(je)001:9008: ye shes bdun 'byung gi rgyud las //
NK097(je)001:9009: 'di la sbyang bgrod yul dang bral //
NK097(je)001:9010: 'di la bsam dpyod mtha' dang bral //
NK097(je)001:9011: 'di la rtsol bsgrub mtha' dang bral //
NK097(je)001:9013: zhes gsungs pa lta bu'i spang blang rtsol sgrub thams
NK097(je)001:9014: cad las 'das pa'i don mthar thug pa ston par
NK097(je)001:9015: byed pas na snying po don gyi theg pa zhes
NK097(je)001:9018: kye 'das pa dang ma byon pa dang da ltar
NK097(je)001:9019: gyi rgyal ba sangs rgyas rnams la chos nyid skye
NK097(je)001:9020: ba med pa sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes
NK097(je)001:9021: 'di las gzhan pa'i chos zhig gzigs shing rtogs par
NK097(je)001:9022: bya ba gang yang med pas ma gzigs shing mi
NK097(je)001:9024: ci'i phyir na dper na me long gi nang du
NK097(je)001:9025: gzugs brnyan ci shar thams cad me long las gzhan
NK097(je)001:9027: rig pa byang sems kyi rtsal las shar ba'i phyi
NK097(je)001:9028: nang 'khor 'das kyi chos ji snyed snang ba thams
NK097(je)001:9029: cad snying po rang byung gi ye shes de las
NK097(je)001:9030: gzhan du gzigs par bya ba ci yang ma grub
NK097(je)001:9031: pa'i phyir dang / snang gzhi'i rig pa de nyid
NK097(je)001:9032: rang ngo shes pa tsam las gzigs shing dgongs par
NK097(je)001:9033: bya ba gzhan ci la yang ltos pa med par
NK097(je)001:9034: 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa mngon du 'gyur
NK097(je)001:9035: pa'i phyir dang / ba'i phyir te / rdzogs pa rang byung gi rgyud las /
NK097(je)001:9036: kun bzang rig pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK097(je)001:9037: sangs rgyas med cing sems can med //
NK097(je)001:9038: lha dang lha min 'dre yang med //
NK097(je)001:9040: rig pa ye shes gcig pu nyid //
NK097(je)001:9043: sems nyid me long gzhi yi sangs rgyas nyid //
NK097(je)001:9044: kun gyi 'char gzhi mi 'gag gzugs brnyan 'dzin //
NK097(je)001:9045: de nyid rang bzhin shes pas gzung 'dzin grol //
NK097(je)001:9046: zhes gsungs pa ltar dus gsum gyi rgyal ba thams
NK097(je)001:9047: cad kyi rtogs bya mthar thug pa ni rig pa
NK097(je)001:9048: rang byung gi ye shes 'di las gzhan med pas
NK097(je)001:9049: so // de lta bu'i ma bcos sems kyi gshis
NK097(je)001:9050: lugs snying po rang byung gi ye shes spros pa'i
NK097(je)001:9051: grwa zur thams cad dang bral bas kun zlum thig
NK097(je)001:9052: le chen po'i rang bzhin de ni g.ya' bral me
NK097(je)001:9053: long dag pa'i ngos ltar gzung 'dzin gyi rnam par
NK097(je)001:9054: rtog pa'i dri ma las 'das shing chos thams cad
NK097(je)001:9055: 'char zhing snang ba'i gzhir gyur pa yin pas na
NK097(je)001:9056: lta ba'i me long zhes su bstan pa yin no
NK097(je)001:9057: so // // klong chen rab 'byams rgyal po las /
NK097(je)001:9058: rab zab rgya che klong yangs mtshan //
NK097(je)001:9059: blta ba'i me long dgongs pa yin //
NK097(je)001:9060: zhes sems nyid mtha' dbus dang bral ba de blta ba'i me long du gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK097(je)001:9062: kye kun byed byang chub kyi sems nga ni chos
NK097(je)001:9063: thams cad kyi gnas lugs ma bcos ji bzhin pa'i
NK097(je)001:9064: rang bzhin snying po rang byung gi ye shes yin
NK097(je)001:9065: la / de nyid ye nas smra bsam brjod du
NK097(je)001:9066: med pa spros pa thams cad dang bral ba'i rang
NK097(je)001:9067: bzhin yin pas de bzhin du yod par sgro 'dogs
NK097(je)001:9068: pa dang med par skur pa 'debas pa'i don las
NK097(je)001:9069: rnam pa kun tu 'das te ngo bo ma bcos
NK097(je)001:9070: bloo las 'das pa'i rang bzhin ji bzhin pa rtogs
NK097(je)001:9071: la / pa'i sgo nas / dus gsum gyi rgyal
NK097(je)001:9072: ba thams cad kun byed nga las 'byung ba yin
NK097(je)001:9073: pa'i rgyu mtshan de bas na dus gsum rgyal ba'i
NK097(je)001:9074: bskyed yum shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin ma
NK097(je)001:9075: zhes su nges par bstan pa yin te /
NK097(je)001:9076: kun tu bzang po che ba rang la gnas pa las /
NK097(je)001:9077: dus gsum bde gshegs bskyed pa'i yum //
NK097(je)001:9078: yum ni shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK097(je)001:9079: mi skye mi 'gag brdal ba la //
NK097(je)001:9080: kun bzang yangs pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK097(je)001:9081: dag go shes rab chen po'i dbyings //
NK097(je)001:9082: 'dzin dang bral lo shes pa med //
NK097(je)001:9083: rtog pa med pas smra bsam 'das //
NK097(je)001:9084: brjod pa med pas nam mkha'i tshul //
NK097(je)001:9085: rang bzhin med pas chos kyi dbyings //
NK097(je)001:9086: phyogs bcur rgya yongs ma chad pa'o //
NK097(je)001:9089: kye gshis lugs 'gyur ba med pa sems nyid rang
NK097(je)001:9090: byung gi ye shes ye nas ma bcos shing ngo
NK097(je)001:9091: bo skye ba med pa'i rang bzhin kun byed rgyal
NK097(je)001:9092: po rig pa byang chub kyi sems 'di nyid la
NK097(je)001:9093: / theg pa 'og ma pa rnams kyis rtsol sgrub
NK097(je)001:9094: sna tshogs pa la brten nas sa lam rim par
NK097(je)001:9095: bgrod pa'i sgo nas thob par byed dgos pa'i lam
NK097(je)001:9096: dang 'bras bu'i yon tan thams cad ma btsal lhun
NK097(je)001:9097: gyis grub pa'i tshul du rdzogs pa yin te /
NK097(je)001:9099: ma bcos rnal du bzhag pa de //
NK097(je)001:9100: theg dman rtsol bsgrub kun 'dus te //
NK097(je)001:9101: 'og min byang chub de la rdzogs //
NK097(je)001:9103: sangs rgyas sa dang pha rol phyin drug rdzogs //
NK097(je)001:9104: tshogs bsags sgrib sbyangs rtsol bsgrub 'bras bu rdzogs //
NK097(je)001:9105: 'gro don mthar phyin phrin las rnam bzhi rdzogs //
NK097(je)001:9106: sems can don byed tshad med rnam bzhi rdzogs //
NK097(je)001:9107: zhes gsungs pa ltar dgos pa'i yon tan thams cad tshang zhing rdzogs pa yin pas /
NK097(je)001:9108: da gdod sku dang ye shes yon tan thams cad
NK097(je)001:9109: btsal zhing bsgrub pa kun las 'das pa yin pas
NK097(je)001:9110: na rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po zhes su bstan
NK097(je)001:9111: pa yin no // snying po don gyi rgyud las /
NK097(je)001:9112: rang byung gcig la yon tan kun tshang bas //
NK097(je)001:9113: ma btsal bzhag pas yon tan rang bzhin rdzogs //
NK097(je)001:9114: ma bsags lhun grub rang byung 'bras bu la //
NK097(je)001:9115: rag las ma yin gdod nas lhun rdzogs yin //
NK097(je)001:9118: kye kun byed rgyal po'i lung 'di ni gnas lugs
NK097(je)001:9119: ma bcos pa'i don la spang blang dgag bsgrub gang
NK097(je)001:9120: yang mi byed par ji bzhin ma nor ba'i blo
NK097(je)001:9122: chos thams cad kyi snying po sems nyid don gyi
NK097(je)001:9123: ye shes la sangs rgyas su sgro 'dogs pa dang
NK097(je)001:9124: sems can gyi rang bzhin du skur pa 'debs pa
NK097(je)001:9126: de lta bu'i sgro skur gyi yul 'khor 'das dang
NK097(je)001:9127: bzang ngan rtag chad la sogs pa'i mthar gnyis ka
NK097(je)001:9128: mnyam nyid blang dor dang bral bas mi 'gal ba'i
NK097(je)001:9129: don du gang zhig ston pa yi theg pa kun
NK097(je)001:9130: gyi yang rtse 'di ma bcos don gyi lung du
NK097(je)001:9133: kye ston pa'i ston pa kun byed rgyal posa nges
NK097(je)001:9134: gsang bla na med pa'i theg pa 'di nyid du
NK097(je)001:9135: lung bstan pa ni ji ltar na chos thams cad
NK097(je)001:9136: gdod nas skye ba med pa snying po byang chub
NK097(je)001:9137: sems kyi rang bzhin du ston pa yin pas rgyud
NK097(je)001:9138: sde 'di nyid la brjod bya de dang ldan pa'i
NK097(je)001:9140: yang na byang chub kyi sems de dang dbyer med
NK097(je)001:9141: du ldan pa'i don snang srid kyi chos thams cad
NK097(je)001:9143: gang ltar yang de lta bu'i skye med byang chub
NK097(je)001:9144: sems kyi klong na gnyis chos su grub pa gang
NK097(je)001:9145: yang med par / 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK097(je)001:9146: snying por ste snying po byang chub kyi sems su
NK097(je)001:9147: gnyis med ro gcig tu gnas par ston pa yin
NK097(je)001:9148: yang med par / pas / rgyud kyi rgyal po
NK097(je)001:9149: chen po 'di la chos rnams kun gyi mdo ni
NK097(je)001:9150: snying po byang chub kyi sems gcig gi rang bzhin
NK097(je)001:9151: du mdo ru bsdus te bstan pa zhes su brjod
NK097(je)001:9152: yang med par / pas / pa yin no //
NK097(je)001:9153: gnyis pa che ba'i yon tan brjod pa la gnyis
NK097(je)001:9154: yang med par / pas / pa yin no //
NK097(je)001:9155: te / mun pa sel zhing snang ba mched pa'i
NK097(je)001:9156: yang med par / pas / pa yin no //
NK097(je)001:9157: te / yon tan / sdug bsngal gcod cing de
NK097(je)001:9158: nyid goms pa'i yon tan no //
NK097(je)001:9160: kye sems dpa' chen po gong du bstan pa de
NK097(je)001:9161: lta bu'i rgyud kyi rgyal po kun byed byang chub
NK097(je)001:9162: sems kyi rang bzhin ma bcos rnal ma'i don ji
NK097(je)001:9163: bzhin du ston par byed pa'i mdo lung zab mo
NK097(je)001:9164: 'di ni / khams gsum gyi 'gro ba kun gyi
NK097(je)001:9165: rgyud la 'di tsam mo zhes thog ma 'jog mi
NK097(je)001:9166: shes pa'i dus yun ring po'i bar du zhugs shing
NK097(je)001:9167: khyab pa'i ma rig pa yi mun pa 'thug po
NK097(je)001:9168: shin tu spang dka' ba'i rang bzhin du gnas pa
NK097(je)001:9169: 'di nyid drung nas 'byin cing skad cig gis sel
NK097(je)001:9170: ba'am 'jom par byed pa'i gnyen po yin zhing /
NK097(je)001:9171: 'khor 'das lam gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK097(je)001:9172: gdod nas skye ba med pa sems nyid rang byung
NK097(je)001:9173: gi ye shes nyag gcig gi rol pa yin kyang
NK097(je)001:9174: / rmig rgyu la chu ru 'khrul pa ltar ma
NK097(je)001:9175: dag mtshan mar zhen cing gzung 'dzin gnyis su snang
NK097(je)001:9176: ba'i 'gro ba thams cad nges don snying po'i lam
NK097(je)001:9178: dper na rin po che gser gling nas sa rdo
NK097(je)001:9179: phal pa btsal kyang mi rnyed pa ltar ji ltar
NK097(je)001:9180: snang grags rtog pa'i chos thams cad la ma dag
NK097(je)001:9181: mtshan ma'i chos rdul phra rab kyi cha tsam yang
NK097(je)001:9182: ma grub par / gang snang ji shar thams cad
NK097(je)001:9183: ye shes nyag gcig gi rol par 'char bar byed
NK097(je)001:9184: pas na ye shes chen po'i snang ba mched par
NK097(je)001:9187: 'di ltar khams gsum rigs drug na rgyu ba'i sems
NK097(je)001:9188: can rnams la med snang 'khrul pa'i rang gzugs su
NK097(je)001:9189: shar ba'i sdug bsngal gyi rnam grangs bsam gyis mi
NK097(je)001:9190: khyab pa ni / gting zab cing thar bar dka' ba /
NK097(je)001:9191: rgya che zhing pha mtha' mi mngon pas rgya mtsho chen po ltar bu yin mod /
NK097(je)001:9192: de lta bu'i sdug bsngal la rtag tu spyod pa'i
NK097(je)001:9193: sems can rnams kyang man ngag zab mo 'di dang
NK097(je)001:9194: 'phrad na dbang po yang rab rnams thos pa tsam
NK097(je)001:9195: gyis skad gcig gcig gis bye brag byed la /
NK097(je)001:9196: de tsam min kyang dbang po 'bring dang tha ma
NK097(je)001:9197: rnams kyang rgyud don zab mo rtogs shing goms pa
NK097(je)001:9198: la brten nas ring por mi thog par /
NK097(je)001:9199: sdug bsngal de thams cad rgyun gcod cing zag med
NK097(je)001:9200: bde ba mchog gi go 'phang la dbang bsgyur cing
NK097(je)001:9201: thob par byed pa yin pa dang /
NK097(je)001:9202: rgyud kyi rgyal po chen po 'di nyid kyis sems
NK097(je)001:9203: nyid rang byung gi ye shes ma bcos rnal ma'i
NK097(je)001:9204: don ma nor rjen cer du bstan par mdzad pa
NK097(je)001:9205: na / rang bzhin babs kyi bsam gtan ngang bzhag
NK097(je)001:9206: chu bo lta bu'i dgongs pa las skad cig kyang
NK097(je)001:9207: g.yengs pa med pas snying po yi don la goms
NK097(je)001:9208: par byed pa'i yon tan gyi che ba dang ldan
NK097(je)001:9209: na / pa yin no // gsum pa de'i don 'dzin pas grub par bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK097(je)001:9210: skye med rtogs pa'i rang bzhin bya btsal med par grol ba dang /
NK097(je)001:9211: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don la yid ches
NK097(je)001:9212: par bzhag pas bcos bsgyur med pa'i ngo bo kun
NK097(je)001:9213: byed nyid mthong bar bstan pa'o //
NK097(je)001:9215: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes de nyid chos
NK097(je)001:9216: thams cad la chos nyid snying po'i tshul du 'du
NK097(je)001:9217: 'bral med par khyab kyang sems can thams cad de'i
NK097(je)001:9218: rang bzhin du ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin na
NK097(je)001:9219: rgyud 'di nyid la ltos ci dgos snyam na /
NK097(je)001:9220: kye sems dpa' rdo rje ston pa kun byed rgyal po ngas ni /
NK097(je)001:9221: gdul bya rnams kyi rgyud na rang gnas snying po
NK097(je)001:9222: ye shes de nyid ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i rang
NK097(je)001:9223: bzhin du skad cig kyang 'bral ma myong bar gdod
NK097(je)001:9224: nas lhan gcig skyes pa'i ngo bor bzhugs nas yod
NK097(je)001:9225: kyang / de nyid lhan skyes dang kun brtags kyi
NK097(je)001:9226: ma rig pa yi ling tog gis shes rab kyi
NK097(je)001:9227: dmigs bu bsgribs nas ma mthong bar med snang 'khor
NK097(je)001:9228: ba'i duhkha la spyod pa rnams kyi ma rig pa'i
NK097(je)001:9229: sgrib pa de dag bsal nas /
NK097(je)001:9230: chos dbyings skye ba med pa rig pa byang chub
NK097(je)001:9231: sems kyi rang zhal ni ma nor ba mngon sum
NK097(je)001:9233: skal ldan gyi rnal 'byor ba sems nyid ma bcos
NK097(je)001:9234: rnal ma'i don ji bzhin mthong ba'i ye shes mig
NK097(je)001:9235: dang ldan pa de dag gis /
NK097(je)001:9236: theg pa 'og ma'i skabs nas bstan pa'i spang blang
NK097(je)001:9237: rtsol bsgrub kyi bya ba gang yang byas pa med
NK097(je)001:9238: par gdod nas ye sangs rgyas pa rang byung 'dus
NK097(je)001:9239: ma byas pa'i rang bzhin 'di nyid skad cig la
NK097(je)001:9240: rtogs nas gdod ma'i ka dag chen po'i klong du
NK097(je)001:9244: de lta bu'i rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po theg
NK097(je)001:9245: pa ma lus pa'i snying po gsang sngags kyi chos
NK097(je)001:9246: yin la de'i kyang snying po theg pa 'di nyid
NK097(je)001:9247: yin pas theg pa'i yang snying chos sku kun byed
NK097(je)001:9248: rgyal po'i dgongs don ji bzhin pa bka' rtsal zhing
NK097(je)001:9249: bstan pa yi man ngag zab mo a ti rdzogs
NK097(je)001:9250: pa chen po 'di lta bu'i man ngag snying po
NK097(je)001:9251: yi lung dang ldan pa'i skal ldan gyi gang zag
NK097(je)001:9252: rnams kyis chos sku kun byed rgyal po'i dgongs don
NK097(je)001:9253: zab mo de la yid ches kyi blo thag gting
NK097(je)001:9255: re dogs 'bad rtsol gyi bya ba ci yang mi
NK097(je)001:9256: byed par sems kyi rang bzhin ma bcos gnyug ma'i
NK097(je)001:9257: ngang la rang bab bcos bsgyur dang bral bar bzhag
NK097(je)001:9258: ste 'bad rtsol gyis gdung ba med par bde bar
NK097(je)001:9259: gnas par byas na chos nyid byang chub sems kyi
NK097(je)001:9260: rang bzhin gdod nas bsal bzhag bral ba'i dgongs pa
NK097(je)001:9261: de nyid bsgrib med mngon sum nyid du gsal bar
NK097(je)001:9263: des na sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes de
NK097(je)001:9264: blang dor 'bad rtsol gyis ma bcos shing rang bzhin
NK097(je)001:9265: mi 'gyur ba'i don ji bzhin pa la 'jug cinga
NK097(je)001:9266: rtsol ba med par lhun rdzogs bde ba chen po'i
NK097(je)001:9267: ngang la gnas par gyis shig ces gdams pa ste
NK097(je)001:9268: / khreg chod rgyab chos nam mkha' rab 'byams las /
NK097(je)001:9269: kye ho grogs dag dran rig 'gyu ba'i sems //
NK097(je)001:9270: bu chung bzhin te rang babs gang dgar thongs //
NK097(je)001:9271: dran bsam 'dzin bral smyon pa'i brtul zhugs can //
NK097(je)001:9272: gang babs gang byung thog babs chen por thongs //
NK097(je)001:9273: rang babs lhod chags rgan po'i ngang tshul can //
NK097(je)001:9274: gzeb bral khod yangs gang shar rang babs thongs //
NK097(je)001:9275: rnal 'byor chen po'i dgongs klong yangs pa yin //
NK097(je)001:9276: sna tshogs dran rig thams cad ye shes dngos //
NK097(je)001:9277: rang shar rang grol kun bzang chos kyi sku //
NK097(je)001:9278: zhes gsungs pa ltar dgag bsgrub dang bcos bsgyur ci
NK097(je)001:9279: yang mi byed par bzhag pas gang shar ci snang
NK097(je)001:9280: thams cad kun byed kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin
NK097(je)001:9282: bzhi pa kun byed snying po'i rgyud skal med la
NK097(je)001:9283: gsang zhing skal ldan la snang ba'i don du sems
NK097(je)001:9284: dpa' rdo rje la gtad pa la gsum ste /
NK097(je)001:9285: sku gsum ston pas dus gsum du ma gsungs pa'i don kun byed ston pas gsungs pa'i tshul /
NK097(je)001:9286: skal med la mi spel zhing skal ldan la snang
NK097(je)001:9287: bas mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan kun byed snying po'i
NK097(je)001:9288: rgyud nges par gtad pa'i tshul lo //
NK097(je)001:9290: kye sems dpa' chen po chos thams cad rtsol med
NK097(je)001:9291: ye sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du ston par mdzad
NK097(je)001:9292: pa po nga ni sku gsum gyi rgyal ba ma
NK097(je)001:9293: lus pa'i ston pa chos sku kun byed rgyal po
NK097(je)001:9294: ste / ston pa ngas bstan pa'i rgyud kyi rgyal
NK097(je)001:9295: po chen po theg pa ma lus pa'i rtsa ba
NK097(je)001:9296: ste / / chos thams cad kyi snying po'i rang
NK097(je)001:9297: bzhin ma nor bar ston pa'i mdo lung gang zhig
NK097(je)001:9298: rgyal ba sku gsum gyi ston pas ma gsungs pa'i
NK097(je)001:9299: bka' zab cing rgya che ba /
NK097(je)001:9300: chos thams cad ye nas skye ba med par rang
NK097(je)001:9301: byung ye shes gcig gi rang bzhin du gnyis med
NK097(je)001:9302: mnyam pa nyid du ston par byed pa'i sems nyid
NK097(je)001:9303: rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyud 'di ni /
NK097(je)001:9304: dus gsum gyi rgyal bas te rgyal ba ma lus
NK097(je)001:9305: pas sngon chad byon zin pa rnams kyis ma gsungs
NK097(je)001:9306: te 'di ni chos sku'i bstan pa yin pa'i phyir
NK097(je)001:9307: ro // de bzhin du phyi ma ste ma 'ongs
NK097(je)001:9308: pa na 'byon par 'gyur ba rnams kyis mi gsung
NK097(je)001:9309: ro // la / da ltar sku dngos su 'tsho
NK097(je)001:9310: zhing bzhugs pa rnams kyis kyang ston par mi mdzad
NK097(je)001:9311: pas a ti rdzogs pa chen po'i theg pa 'di
NK097(je)001:9312: dang shin tu 'phrad dka' ba yin phyir man ngag
NK097(je)001:9313: snying po'i don dang da ris 'phrad pa'i dus 'dir
NK097(je)001:9314: gces spras kyis nan tan byed par gdams pa yang
NK097(je)001:9317: de ltar dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas rnams kyis ma gsungs na /
NK097(je)001:9318: 'o na ston pa gang gis gsungs pa yin zhe na /
NK097(je)001:9319: 'di nyid gsungs pa po ni sku gsum gyi rgyal
NK097(je)001:9320: ba ma lus pa'i ston pa dus gsum sangs rgyas
NK097(je)001:9321: kun gyi spyi mes chen po dang po'i sangs rgyas
NK097(je)001:9323: rang byung kun tu bzang po chos sku kun byed rgyal posa gsungs pa yin la /
NK097(je)001:9324: de lta bu'i ston pa rang byung gi ye shes
NK097(je)001:9325: de ni dmigs mtshan spros pa thams cad las 'das
NK097(je)001:9326: shing rtag tu 'pho 'gyur mi mnga' ba yin pas
NK097(je)001:9327: / ston pa kun byed nyid kyis ni gsang chen
NK097(je)001:9328: a ti'i theg pa 'di nyid snga bar te sngar
NK097(je)001:9329: yang gsungs shing phyis kyang gsungs bar 'gyur la /
NK097(je)001:9330: da ltar mngon sum du byunga bar gyur pa 'di
NK097(je)001:9331: nyid na'ang gsungs pa yin pas zhes don la sangs
NK097(je)001:9332: rgyas chos kyi sku la dus gsum gyi dbye ba
NK097(je)001:9333: med kyang dus bzhi mnyams pa nyid kyi ngang na
NK097(je)001:9334: rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lor gsungs pa yin par
NK097(je)001:9336: de ltar ston pa kun byed rgyal pos skal ldan
NK097(je)001:9337: gyi gdul bya dbang po yang rab rnams la chos
NK097(je)001:9338: sgo thams cad kyi nang nas nges pa'i snying po
NK097(je)001:9339: dam par gyur pa dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas rnams
NK097(je)001:9340: kyis ma gsungs mi gsung gsung bar mi 'gyur ba'i
NK097(je)001:9341: theg mchog rdzogs pa chen po'i dgongs don snying po
NK097(je)001:9342: byang chub sems kyi don ma nor bar bstan pas
NK097(je)001:9343: dka' spyod dang rtsol sgrub la ltos pa med par
NK097(je)001:9344: 'bad med du grol ba'i lung zab mo //
NK097(je)001:9345: kun byed byang chub sems kyi mdo lung ltar sems
NK097(je)001:9346: dpa' rdo rje nyid la mngon sum du bstan pa'i
NK097(je)001:9347: bka' rgyud thams cad kyi snying po mthar thug pa
NK097(je)001:9348: 'di nyid / skal med sgro skur 'debs pa'i rigs
NK097(je)001:9349: can rnams la sba zhing gsang ba'i sgo nas kun
NK097(je)001:9350: la mi 'phel ba'am mi spel ba dang /
NK097(je)001:9351: skal ldan rnams la nges gsang bstan pa'i snang ba
NK097(je)001:9352: mi nub par byed pa'i dgos pa yod pas theg
NK097(je)001:9353: mchog rdo rje snying po 'di yi bstan pa 'dzin
NK097(je)001:9354: par byed pa rnams la ston zhing spel bar byed
NK097(je)001:9355: pa'i ched du / bstan pa'i snying po chos nyid
NK097(je)001:9356: mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan kun byed rgyal po mchog
NK097(je)001:9357: gi rgyud 'di nyid sgro skur dang bral bar nges
NK097(je)001:9359: thugs sras dam pa sems dpa' rdo rje khyod la gtad do //
NK097(je)001:9362: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po las mtshan
NK097(je)001:9363: gyi rnam grangs bstan pa'i le'u ste brgyad cu rtsa
NK097(je)001:9364: bzhi pa'i 'grel pa'o ////spyi don gsum pa yongs su
NK097(je)001:9365: rdzogs pa'i don la gnyis te /
NK097(je)001:9366: gang yongs su rdzogs pa'i rgyud dang /
NK097(je)001:9367: gang gis bsgyur zhing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o //
NK097(je)001:9374: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po zhes pa
NK097(je)001:9375: theg pa 'og ma rnams las brjod bya shin tu
NK097(je)001:9376: zab cing rgya che bas phul du phyin pa mtshon
NK097(je)001:9377: par byed pa'i mtshan gyi khyad par bstan pa'o //
NK097(je)001:9379: de lta bu'i mtshan gyi khyad par dang ldan pa'i
NK097(je)001:9380: rgyud kyi rgyal po chen po 'di nyid kyi brjod
NK097(je)001:9381: bya 'od gsal rdzogs pa chen po'i lta ba'am rig
NK097(je)001:9382: pa byang chub sems kyi ngo bo ni nam mkha'
NK097(je)001:9383: ltar 'khor 'das thams cad la khyab pas rgya che
NK097(je)001:9384: zhing mtha' dang dbus med pas smra brjod spros pa
NK097(je)001:9385: thams cad dang bral ba'i rang bzhin yin la de
NK097(je)001:9386: nyid ji lta ba bzhin bstan par mdzad pa'i rgyud
NK097(je)001:9387: 'di yang bcos bsgyur spang blang las 'das pa'i rang
NK097(je)001:9388: bzhin can te / snying po don gyi rgyud las bskyed pa med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK097(je)001:9390: gang la'ang mi brtan rtog dpyod 'das //
NK097(je)001:9391: ma bcos rdzogs pa'i theg par gsungs //
NK097(je)001:9394: de lta bu'i smra bsam brjod du med pa'i chos
NK097(je)001:9395: nyid byang chub kyi sems nam mkha' lta bu de
NK097(je)001:9396: yang stong pa phyang chad pa lta bu ma yin
NK097(je)001:9397: par lhun grub 'od gsal ba'i ye shes dang 'du
NK097(je)001:9398: 'bral med pas 'khor 'das kyi snang cha mu med
NK097(je)001:9399: par 'char du yod pas nam mkha'i snying po mchog
NK097(je)001:9402: ma skyes snying po sgro skur med pa'i dbyings //
NK097(je)001:9403: sangs rgyas sems can ma skyes snying por mthong //
NK097(je)001:9406: de lta bu'i gsang ba mchog gi don ma nor
NK097(je)001:9407: ba ston par mdzad pa'i mdo lung chen po le'u
NK097(je)001:9408: brgyad cu rtsa bzhi pa rdzogs so //
NK097(je)001:9409: zhes yongs su rdzogs pa mthar phyin par bstan pa'o //
NK097(je)001:9410: gnyis pa gang gis bsgyur zhing zhus de gtan la phab pa la gsum ste /
NK097(je)001:9411: pan+di ta gang gis bsgyur ba /
NK097(je)001:9412: lo ts+aa ba gang gis zhus pa /
NK097(je)001:9413: chos gang gtan la phab pa'o //
NK097(je)001:9415: rgya gar gyi mkhan po dpa' gyi seng ge mgon po dang zhes pa ni pan+di ta'i mtshan te /
NK097(je)001:9416: de la bdag nyid chen po 'di ni ma h+aa
NK097(je)001:9417: tsi na'i yul gyi grong khyer sho 'khyams nag po
NK097(je)001:9418: zhes bya bar yab khyim bdag dge ldan bzang po
NK097(je)001:9419: dang yum snang gsal ldan ma'i sras sh+r+ai seng ha
NK097(je)001:9420: zhes bya bar sku 'khrungs te sgra tshad la sogs
NK097(je)001:9421: pa'i rig pa'i gnas lnga la mkhas shing /
NK097(je)001:9422: gsang sngags phyi nang gi rgyud lung man ngag thams
NK097(je)001:9423: cad thugs su chud pa'i mkhas pa chen po zhig
NK097(je)001:9425: re zhig gi tshe na 'phags mchog mig gi 'dzum
NK097(je)001:9426: pa mdun gyi nam mkhar byon nas lung bstan pa
NK097(je)001:9427: / kye skal ldan tshe gcig gis 'bras bu nges
NK097(je)001:9428: par 'dod na dur khrod chen po bsil ba'i tshal
NK097(je)001:9429: du song zhig ces gsungs pas /
NK097(je)001:9430: rkang mgyogs kyi rdzu 'phrul la brten nas nyin mtshan
NK097(je)001:9431: dgu na dur khrod chen po bsil ba'i tshal du
NK097(je)001:9432: byon pas / der slob dpon chen po dga' rab
NK097(je)001:9433: rdo rje dang mjal nas phyag 'tshal te zhabs spyi
NK097(je)001:9434: bor blangs shing bdag rjes su 'dzin par zhus pas
NK097(je)001:9435: byon pas / gnang ste / lo nyi shu rtsa
NK097(je)001:9436: lngar thig le mchog gi rgyud lung man ngag dang
NK097(je)001:9437: bcas pa'i dbang khrid thams cad zhus shing nyams su
NK097(je)001:9438: blang bas 'od gsal chu yi zla ba lta bu'i
NK097(je)001:9439: lus thob nas mchog gi dngos grub brnyes par gyur
NK097(je)001:9440: byon pas / gnang ste / pas mtshon / mdor
NK097(je)001:9441: na pan+di ta lnga brgya'i thugs sras su gyur zhing
NK097(je)001:9442: mkhas grub yongs kyi gtsug rgyan chen por gyur pa
NK097(je)001:9443: byon pas / gnang ste / pas mtshon / de nyid do // gnyis pa ni /
NK097(je)001:9445: bee ro tsa na 'dra ba'i lo ts+wa ba //
NK097(je)001:9446: sngar yang ma byon da yang 'byon re kan //
NK097(je)001:9447: lo ts+wa zhes kyang don la pan+di ta //
NK097(je)001:9450: bee ro tsa na nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK097(je)001:9451: rka cog zhang gsum nyi zla zung 'brel 'dra //
NK097(je)001:9452: rin chen bzang po tho rang skar rjen tsam //
NK097(je)001:9453: kho bo cag ni srin bu me khyer 'dra //
NK097(je)001:9454: zhes gsungs pa sogs don gzigs kyi skyes bu rnams
NK097(je)001:9455: kyis basngagasa pa'i me tog yang yang 'thor ba dang
NK097(je)001:9456: / rje bee ro nyid kyi zhal nas kyang /
NK097(je)001:9457: gson dang bod kyi rje 'bangs rjes 'jug tsho //
NK097(je)001:9458: bee ro nga yi gtam gcig bshad //
NK097(je)001:9459: lo brgyad lon nas bcu gsum bar //
NK097(je)001:9460: skad rigs mi gcig gsum brgya drug cu slabs //
NK097(je)001:9461: bcu bzhi lon nas rgya gar yul du byon //
NK097(je)001:9462: dga' rab 'jam dpal sh+r+ai ri seng ha sogs //
NK097(je)001:9463: 'ja' lus grub pa nyi shu rtsa lnga brten //
NK097(je)001:9464: mkhas grub brnyes pa bdun cu rtsa gnyis brten //
NK097(je)001:9465: do shi do chad dka' ba sna tshogs spyad //
NK097(je)001:9466: rgya chos lhag med ma lus bod du bsgyur //
NK097(je)001:9467: zhes sogs gsungs pas mtshan yon tan gyi che ba
NK097(je)001:9468: blos gzhan du mi nus pa dang ldan pa'i skad
NK097(je)001:9469: gnyis smra ba'i khyu mchog chen po dge slong bee
NK097(je)001:9470: ro tsa nas zhes pa ni bsgyur byed lo ts+wa
NK097(je)001:9471: ba'i mtshan no // gsum pa nang gses su gsum las /
NK097(je)001:9473: rgya dpe las bod dper bsgyur cing /
NK097(je)001:9474: gnyis pa bod dpe las rgya dper zhus te dag par byas pa dang /
NK097(je)001:9475: gsum pa ni slar tshig 'chad nyan gyi sgo nas
NK097(je)001:9476: rgya dpe las ji ltar bstan pa ltar bod dper
NK097(je)001:9477: te bod dpe'i steng nas gtan la phab nas shin
NK097(je)001:9479: de lta bu'i theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse
NK097(je)001:9480: dang chos thams cad kyi snying por gyur pa'i nges
NK097(je)001:9481: gsang rdzogs chen po'i bstan pa 'di nyid lnga brgya'i
NK097(je)001:9482: tha ma la byang phyogs kha ba can gyi yul
NK097(je)001:9483: ljongs su dar nas 'gro ba'i sgron me chen po
NK097(je)001:9485: rang byung bde ba'i 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK097(je)001:9486: dus kyi tha ma lnga brgya na //
NK097(je)001:9488: mtshon dang mu ge tshe thung dus //
NK097(je)001:9489: rdzogs chen snying por dus der bshad //
NK097(je)001:9490: de yang rdo rje sems dpa' nyon //
NK097(je)001:9491: de dang dus kyi deng sang na //
NK097(je)001:9492: sangs rgyas bstan pa 'jig pa'i tshe //
NK097(je)001:9493: 'dzam gling bod kyi byang phyogs su //
NK097(je)001:9494: lung dang tan tra mang po 'byung //
NK097(je)001:9495: lung dang sems kyi chos dar ste //
NK097(je)001:9496: sde snod chos kun nub 'gyur zhing //
NK097(je)001:9498: rang sems rtogs pa tsam gyis ni //
NK097(je)001:9501: ye shes gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NK097(je)001:9502: rtsol bral gsang ba'i theg pa 'di //
NK097(je)001:9503: lha gnas gsum du grags gyur nas //
NK097(je)001:9504: yang sprul gang zag thugs sras kyis //
NK097(je)001:9505: 'dzam gling dbus su rgyas par byed //
NK097(je)001:9506: rgyal sras gsang ba'i snod ldan la //
NK097(je)001:9507: rnar brgyud rim pa sngags kyi don //
NK097(je)001:9508: 'phrul tshig rig pa'i sgo nas bstan //
NK097(je)001:9509: gsang 'dzin rig pa'i snod ldan rnams //
NK097(je)001:9510: ma bcos gsang ba'i don go nas //
NK097(je)001:9512: de nas gsang ba dam pa 'di //
NK097(je)001:9514: der yang gsang ba dam pa 'di //
NK097(je)001:9515: skal ldan gdul bya'i ngo dag tu //
NK097(je)001:9516: rig pa'i sgron me byed par 'gyur //
NK097(je)001:9518: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa las /
NK097(je)001:9519: de nas thugs rje'i byin rlabs dang //
NK097(je)001:9520: dad pas las 'phro ldan pa yi //
NK097(je)001:9521: gnyis su med par mthun pa yis //
NK097(je)001:9522: mtha' 'khob yul du snang gyur nas //
NK097(je)001:9523: skal ldan rigs rgyud 'dzin pa rnams //
NK097(je)001:9524: rang gsal rig pa'i don go nas //
NK097(je)001:9525: sangs rgyas sa la bgrod par 'gyur //
NK097(je)001:9526: 'di rnams dad ldan rgyal sras te //
NK097(je)001:9527: rigs su nges pa nyid du 'gyur //
NK097(je)001:9528: zhes gsungs pa de ltar rgyal ba kun tu bzang
NK097(je)001:9529: pos bslu med rdo rje'i gsung gis ji ltar lung
NK097(je)001:9530: bstan pa bzhin du lo pan sprul pa'i skyes mchog
NK097(je)001:9531: rnams kyi thugs bskyed dus su sad pa'i mthu la
NK097(je)001:9532: brten nas / sangs rgyas las kyang 'phrad par dka'
NK097(je)001:9533: ba'i chos zab pa las kyang ches zab pa nges
NK097(je)001:9534: gsang rdzogs pa chen po sems lung man ngag gi
NK097(je)001:9535: rgyud thams cad gangs ljongs gdul bya'i dpal du spyan
NK097(je)001:9536: brten nas / drangs shing / kun gzigs rong klong
NK097(je)001:9537: rnam gnyis sogs dgongs pa'i rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i grub
NK097(je)001:9538: pa'i rig 'dzin chen po rnams kyis dgongs 'grel gyi
NK097(je)001:9539: bstan bcos kyang mang du mdzad pa'i bka' drin la
NK097(je)001:9540: brten nas / drangs shing / brten nas / deng
NK097(je)001:9541: sang dus kyi snyigs ma la bab pa'i skabs 'dir
NK097(je)001:9542: yang lnga bdo'i rgud pas mnar ba'i sems can bdag
NK097(je)001:9543: dang bdag lta bu rnams yin yang theg mchog 'od
NK097(je)001:9544: gsal rdzogs chen po'i chos la spyod du yod pa'i
NK097(je)001:9545: skal bzang thob pa 'di la dga' spro dang bcas
NK097(je)001:9546: pas 'chad nyan bsgom pa sogs la brtson par byas
NK097(je)001:9547: na yon tan dpag tu med pa dang ldan par
NK097(je)001:9548: brten nas / drangs shing / brten nas / gsungs
NK097(je)001:9549: te / rang byung bde ba 'khor lo'i rgyud las
NK097(je)001:9550: brten nas / drangs shing / brten nas / gsungs
NK097(je)001:9551: te / / dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad pas
NK097(je)001:9552: brten nas / drangs shing / brten nas / gsungs
NK097(je)001:9553: te / / // kun bzang dgongs pa che ba
NK097(je)001:9554: brten nas / drangs shing / brten nas / gsungs
NK097(je)001:9555: te / / // yin // theg gzhan chos kun
NK097(je)001:9556: brten nas / drangs shing / brten nas / gsungs
NK097(je)001:9558: rdzogs chen mos pa khyad par 'phags //
NK097(je)001:9561: 'di yi phan yon bsam yas te //
NK097(je)001:9562: re zhig mtshon pa tsam bstan pa //
NK097(je)001:9563: gnas su bcing bas bar chad bsrung //
NK097(je)001:9564: lus la bcing bas sgrib gnyis sel //
NK097(je)001:9565: bklag pa tsam gyis tshogs gnyis rdzogs //
NK097(je)001:9566: mthong ba tsam gyis don dang 'phrad //
NK097(je)001:9567: thos pa tsam gyis spros thag chod //
NK097(je)001:9568: bzung bas chos kun bzung dang mtshungs //
NK097(je)001:9569: skal par bsags pa'i sgrib pa yang //
NK097(je)001:9570: 'di ni rna bar thos pas sel //
NK097(je)001:9571: mos pa byas pa tsam la yang //
NK097(je)001:9572: sa bcu'i sras dang yon tan mnyam //
NK097(je)001:9574: yon tan bsam dang brjod las 'das //
NK097(je)001:9575: yid bzhin nor bu rin chen 'dra //
NK097(je)001:9577: rin po che spungs pa las /
NK097(je)001:9579: rang rig rnams kyis dbang thob ste //
NK097(je)001:9580: rgyud 'di bcing ba tsam gyis kyang //
NK097(je)001:9582: rgyud 'di su yis bklag pa'i mi //
NK097(je)001:9583: lta ba'i don kun sems la 'char //
NK097(je)001:9584: 'di nyid su yi bris pa ste //
NK097(je)001:9585: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung la rol //
NK097(je)001:9586: de yi phyir na dam par byos //
NK097(je)001:9589: nges don 'di la gang mos rnams //
NK097(je)001:9590: bka' dang mthun par don go nas //
NK097(je)001:9591: rdul tsam du yang ma bsgom kyang //
NK097(je)001:9592: sangs rgyas sa la smos ci dgos //
NK097(je)001:9596: sangs rgyas kun gyis byin gyis rlabs //
NK097(je)001:9597: bsod nams mi zad gter dang mjal //
NK097(je)001:9599: kun tu bzang pos de skad bshad //
NK097(je)001:9601: rin po che rgyas pa chen po'i rgyud las /
NK097(je)001:9602: ston pa'i ston pa kun tu bzang po des //
NK097(je)001:9603: sdud pa'i gsang dbang rdo rje sems dpa' la //
NK097(je)001:9604: theg pa 'di la mos pa kun //
NK097(je)001:9605: ma nor dam pa'i lam zhugs nas //
NK097(je)001:9606: sems bskyed pa yi 'bras bu rdzogs //
NK097(je)001:9607: srid pa gar 'byung gar skyes yang //
NK097(je)001:9608: bar do rnam pa gsum nyid du //
NK097(je)001:9610: bla ma lta bur lung yang ston //
NK097(je)001:9611: 'di nyid bris pa tsam gyis su //
NK097(je)001:9612: ngan song rnams las rab rgyal zhing //
NK097(je)001:9613: bde gshegs kun gyis byin gyis brlab //
NK097(je)001:9614: sras kyi dam pa sangs rgyas sras //
NK097(je)001:9616: 'di nyid bklags pa tsam gyis su //
NK097(je)001:9617: khams gsum rnams las rab 'das shing //
NK097(je)001:9618: 'chi ka'i rna bug brjod pa na //
NK097(je)001:9619: ngan song las ni thar bar byed //
NK097(je)001:9620: mi min gdon la sogs pa yis //
NK097(je)001:9621: gdug pa zhi nas yang dag 'thob //
NK097(je)001:9622: lha dang mkha' 'gro thams cad kyis //
NK097(je)001:9623: rje bor mthong nas nges par bkur //
NK097(je)001:9624: yang dag nges pa'i lung yang ston //
NK097(je)001:9625: 'di nyid bcang ba tsam gyis su //
NK097(je)001:9626: ngan song gsum las rab thar zhing //
NK097(je)001:9628: don rnams thams cad 'grub par byed //
NK097(je)001:9629: 'di nyid yid la byed pa yis //
NK097(je)001:9630: bde gshegs thams cad bkur bas na //
NK097(je)001:9631: yang dag lam na gnas pa na //
NK097(je)001:9632: byang chub sems dpas byin gyis rlobs //
NK097(je)001:9633: 'di nyid nyan pa tsam gyis su //
NK097(je)001:9634: theg pa thams cad nyan pas na //
NK097(je)001:9635: sangs rgyas dgongs pa kun 'grub pas //
NK097(je)001:9636: mthun pa'i ye shes rang snang bas //
NK097(je)001:9637: sangs rgyas rnams kyis sras su mthong //
NK097(je)001:9638: byang sems kun gyis spun du gzigs //
NK097(je)001:9639: mkha' 'gro rnams kyis byin gyis brlab //
NK097(je)001:9640: gar 'byung de ni gar skyes yang //
NK097(je)001:9641: theg pa 'di la rtag tu spyod //
NK097(je)001:9642: 'di nyid bshad pa tsam gyis su //
NK097(je)001:9643: dus gsum rgyun mi 'chad pa ru //
NK097(je)001:9644: rtag tu chos kyi 'khor lo bskor //
NK097(je)001:9645: bar do rnam pa gsum du yang //
NK097(je)001:9646: bde gshegs thugs kyis dam par gzigs //
NK097(je)001:9647: rdo rje sems dpa' dngos su snang //
NK097(je)001:9648: 'di yi lung nyid bstan nas ni //
NK097(je)001:9649: yang dag nges pa'i 'bras bu thob //
NK097(je)001:9650: de nyid bsgoms pa tsam gyis su //
NK097(je)001:9651: tshe gcig yang dag 'bras bu ster //
NK097(je)001:9652: sku gsum snang bar lhun gyis grub //
NK097(je)001:9653: de yi yon tan bsam mi khyab //
NK097(je)001:9654: 'di nyid mchod bstod byas pa yin //
NK097(je)001:9655: dkon mchog gsum po kun mchod dang //
NK097(je)001:9656: nye ba'i sras kyi dam par 'dzin //
NK097(je)001:9657: sdug bsngal rnams ni mi 'byung zhing //
NK097(je)001:9658: dbul ba thams cad sel ba'o //
NK097(je)001:9659: stong gsum rdul ni bsam nus te //
NK097(je)001:9660: 'di yi bsod nams bsam mi nus //
NK097(je)001:9661: zhes pa la sogs pa rdzogs chen gyi rgyud sde
NK097(je)001:9662: rnams nas chos zab mo 'di la 'chad nyan bsgoms
NK097(je)001:9663: pa byas pa lta ci smos kyi tha na mos
NK097(je)001:9664: pa tsam byas pa'i bsod nams bsam gyis mi khyab
NK097(je)001:9665: par gsungs pa'i tshul la bsam te rgyal ba kun
NK097(je)001:9666: tu bzang po'i dgongs pa'i gsang mdzod 'di la ci
NK097(je)001:9667: nus su brtson pa ni dal 'byor gyi lus rten
NK097(je)001:9668: thob pa'i don 'bras yang dag pa yin no zhes
NK097(je)001:9669: dang po'i las can rang dang skal ba mnyam pa
NK097(je)001:9670: rnams la zhar byung du thal lo //
NK097(je)001:9671: de ltar kun byed byang chub snying po'i rgyud //
NK097(je)001:9672: mtha' dang dbus med nam mkha' lta bu'i don //
NK097(je)001:9673: deng sang bdag gis phyes pa'i bsod nams des //
NK097(je)001:9674: 'gro kun kun byed rgyal po'i gnas thob shog /da ni rgyal ba'i bstan pa'ang nub tu nye //
NK097(je)001:9675: zab mo'i chos tshul rgya mtsho 'grib la ltos //
NK097(je)001:9676: snyigs dus skye bo shin tu gdul dka' bas //
NK097(je)001:9677: nges don snying po'i don la mos pa nyung //
NK097(je)001:9678: sngon gyi skyes bu dam pa'i bka' drin gyis //
NK097(je)001:9679: rgyud rgyal nyi ma dri med shar na yang //
NK097(je)001:9680: dngangs shing skrag la log ltas dor ba mang //
NK097(je)001:9681: dngos pos mtshan mar zhen pa snying re rje //
NK097(je)001:9682: bag chags gnyis su 'dzin pa'i chos rnams kyis //
NK097(je)001:9683: nam yang srid las mi thar skyo ba 'phel //
NK097(je)001:9684: snying po'i sems nyid mngon sum bltar yod kyang //
NK097(je)001:9685: skal mang dus la ltos pa snying re rje //
NK097(je)001:9686: de 'dra'i 'gro la zab mo'i chos rnams kyis //
NK097(je)001:9687: de nyid rtogs pa'i rang bzhin skal pa chad //
NK097(je)001:9688: de dag mthong nas snying rje'i rlabs g.yos pas //
NK097(je)001:9689: de don bdag gis nam zhig byed par shog /skye ba sngon nas sbyangs pa'i las 'phro can //
NK097(je)001:9690: skal bzang slob ma dam pas bskul ba'i ngor //
NK097(je)001:9691: kun byed rgyud don gsal ba'i rnam bshad 'di //
NK097(je)001:9692: gangs ri thod dkar mgur du legs par bkod //
NK097(je)001:9693: kun byed rgyal po'i rgyud kyi bsdus don nyi zla'i d+r+wa ba zhes bya ba //
NK097(je)001:9694: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK097(je)001:9695: klong chen rab 'byams kyis sbyar ba rdzogs so //
NK097(je)001:9699: zhes pa ni bsdus don gyi mdzad byang ngo //
NK097(je)001:9701: de ltar sku gsum rgyal ba ma lus pa'i //
NK097(je)001:9702: ston pa'i ston pa kun byed rgyal po zhes //
NK097(je)001:9703: ye nas 'khrul ma myong ba'i sangs rgyas des //
NK097(je)001:9704: rang snang rig pa'i 'khor tshogs rgya mtsho la //
NK097(je)001:9705: chos sku'i dgongs pas byin gyis brlabs pa'i tshe //
NK097(je)001:9706: gzhom med rdo rje'i rang sgras bstan pa yi //
NK097(je)001:9707: theg pa'i yang rtse 'od gsal rdzogs pa che //
NK097(je)001:9708: brgyad khri bzhi stong chos kyi snying po mchog /
NK097(je)001:9709: 'di ni dus gsum rgyal ba'i gshegs shul yin //
NK097(je)001:9710: 'di ni rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i thugs bcud yin //
NK097(je)001:9711: 'di ni man ngag kun gyi nying khu yin //
NK097(je)001:9712: 'di dang 'phrad rnams srid pa tha mar gsungs //
NK097(je)001:9713: dus gsum rgyal ba thams cad zhal bsdur kyang //
NK097(je)001:9714: dgongs pa'i zhe phug 'di las gzhan na med //
NK097(je)001:9715: brgyad khri bzhi stong chos rnams go bsdur kyang //
NK097(je)001:9716: nges don zab mo 'di las log na med //
NK097(je)001:9717: theg pa'i rnam grangs ji snyed bsam yas kyang //
NK097(je)001:9718: 'di las gzhan du theg pa'i yang rtse med //
NK097(je)001:9719: lam gyi 'jug sgo ji snyed mchis na yang //
NK097(je)001:9720: myur lam zab mo 'di las lhag pa gang //
NK097(je)001:9721: yun ring dus nas 'bad pa drag po yis //
NK097(je)001:9722: rtsol bcas theg pa'i lam la sbyang ba yi //
NK097(je)001:9723: grub pa'i 'bras bu 'di ru mthar phyin pas //
NK097(je)001:9724: 'di ni theg pa yin la 'bras bu'ang yin //
NK097(je)001:9725: blo 'das bya rtsol bral ba'i dgongs pa yis //
NK097(je)001:9726: yid dpyod mtshan ma'i spros pa ma lus kun //
NK097(je)001:9727: spros med mnyam pa chen por gcod byed pa'i //
NK097(je)001:9728: theg pa'i mchog 'di rno ngar ral gri 'dra //
NK097(je)001:9729: rang gnas chos sku'i rang zhal rjen pa ru //
NK097(je)001:9730: mngon sum thad kar ston pa'i man ngag gis //
NK097(je)001:9731: gnyis snang 'khrul pa'i mun pa drung 'byin pas //
NK097(je)001:9732: theg pa'i mchog 'di snang byed nyi ma 'dra //
NK097(je)001:9733: srid gsum ka dag chen po'i dgongs pa yis //
NK097(je)001:9734: 'khor 'das ming med chen po la bzla zhing //
NK097(je)001:9735: sdug bsngal zug rngu'i tsha gdung sel byed pa'i //
NK097(je)001:9736: theg pa'i mchog 'di 'od dkar zla ba 'dra //
NK097(je)001:9737: rtsol bral ke la sha ri'i rtse mo nas //
NK097(je)001:9738: byar med gdong lnga'i rang skad gcig bton pas //
NK097(je)001:9739: theg dman wa skyes khyu tshogs zil gnon pa'i //
NK097(je)001:9740: theg pa'i mchog 'di gangs dkar seng ge 'dra //
NK097(je)001:9741: ye grol 'dab gshogs rdzogs pa'i rtsal shugs kyis //
NK097(je)001:9742: rigs drug 'khor ba'i g.yang sa gcod byed cing //
NK097(je)001:9743: sems 'dzin rmongs pa'i klu rnams zil gnon pa'i //
NK097(je)001:9744: theg pa'i mchog 'di mkha' lding khyung chen 'dra //
NK097(je)001:9745: rgyal kun dgongs pa'i chu bo ma lus pa //
NK097(je)001:9746: gnyis med ro gcig 'khyil ba'i chu gter che //
NK097(je)001:9747: rig 'dzin klu dbang ma lus rol ba'i gnas //
NK097(je)001:9748: theg pa'i mchog 'di rgya mcho chen po 'dra //
NK097(je)001:9749: ma bcos rang bab chen po'i shugs 'gros kyis //
NK097(je)001:9750: sa lam ma lus mig 'phrul bzhin bgrod pa'i //
NK097(je)001:9751: rdzu 'phrul rkang pa'i mchog dang ldan pa yi //
NK097(je)001:9752: theg pa'i mchog 'di cang shes rta mchog 'dra //
NK097(je)001:9753: zag med rang ngo shes pa'i rig pa la //
NK097(je)001:9754: tshogs gnyis yon tan ma lus lhun rdzogs shing //
NK097(je)001:9755: don gnyis 'dod dgu'i gru char 'beb byed pa'i //
NK097(je)001:9756: theg pa'i mchog 'di yid bzhin nor bu 'dra //
NK097(je)001:9757: de phyir da res dal 'byor mi lus nyid //
NK097(je)001:9758: thob nas yang zab snying po 'di 'phrad tshe //
NK097(je)001:9759: rtsol bcas theg pa'i 'ching ba rab bkrol nas //
NK097(je)001:9760: rtsol med lam 'dir 'jug pa'i dus min nam //
NK097(je)001:9761: kye ma sdug bsngal rgya mtsho gting re zab //
NK097(je)001:9762: las nyon drag po'i rba rlabs shugs re drag /rigs drug 'khor ba'i g.yang sa ya re nga //
NK097(je)001:9763: der gnas ma rgan 'gro rnams snying re rje //
NK097(je)001:9764: mi bzod snying rje'i blo 'dis rab bskul nas //
NK097(je)001:9765: da res rang gzhan 'khor ba'i sems can kun //
NK097(je)001:9766: phyam gcig kun byed chos sku'i dgongs klong du //
NK097(je)001:9767: dgrol phyir snying po'i bstan 'dir 'jug 'dod pa'i //
NK097(je)001:9768: mi ldog dad dang spro ba yod na yang //
NK097(je)001:9769: rang nyams bstun pa'i nyams len cung re la //
NK097(je)001:9770: brtson pa'i nus pa byung na de ka rang //
NK097(je)001:9771: de las gzhan du 'grel bshad rtsom pa sogs //
NK097(je)001:9772: blo chen 'phags pa'i spyod yul ma gtogs par //
NK097(je)001:9773: rnam dpyod shes rab shin tu nyag phra ba'i //
NK097(je)001:9774: byis pa'i blo can bdag 'dra'i yul min bzhin //
NK097(je)001:9775: mi theg khur du len 'di mi mdzes kyang //
NK097(je)001:9776: rigs kyi khyab bdag rdo rje 'chang dbang ngos //
NK097(je)001:9777: rtsa ba'i bla ma theg mchog bstan 'dzin dang //
NK097(je)001:9778: mkhas btsun yon tan rgya mtsho'i mnga' bdag mchog /mkhan chen o t+ai'i mtshan can rnam gnyis kyis //
NK097(je)001:9779: bka' lung gser gyis co pan rab lci ba //
NK097(je)001:9780: dman pa bdag gi gtsug tu bcing ba'i mod //
NK097(je)001:9781: dam pa'i gsung ngag ldog tu mi spobs pas //
NK097(je)001:9782: kun bzang thugs kyi dgongs rgyan 'di brtsam kyang //
NK097(je)001:9783: sngon nas sbyangs pa'i las 'phro bdag la med //
NK097(je)001:9784: da lta'i skyes stobs shes rab bdag la med //
NK097(je)001:9785: zab mo'i don la nyams myong bdag la med //
NK097(je)001:9786: de phyir tshul 'di bdag 'dras rtogs dka' bas //
NK097(je)001:9787: ma rtogs 'khrul pa'i nongs pa gang mchis pa //
NK097(je)001:9788: brgyud gsum rig 'dzin rgya mtsho'i tshogs rnams dang //
NK097(je)001:9789: sde gsum bsrung ma'i tshogs la mthol bshags na //
NK097(je)001:9790: dag tshangs chen po'i dngos grub bdag la zhu //
NK097(je)001:9791: 'di la mos pa tsam gyis bsod nams yang //
NK097(je)001:9792: tshad med bsam mi khyab par basngagasa pa bzhin //
NK097(je)001:9793: 'dir 'bad bsod nams dge tshogs rgya mtsho'i mthus //
NK097(je)001:9794: 'gro kun phan bde'i dpal la spyod gyur cig /sku drin che ba'i bshes gnyen dam pa zung //
NK097(je)001:9795: dag pa'i zhing mchog gang na bzhugs gyur kyang //
NK097(je)001:9796: legs bshad mchod pa'i sprin 'dis dgyes bskangs nas //
NK097(je)001:9797: thugs kyi dgongs pa yongs su rdzogs gyur cig /mtha' med srid pa'i rgya mtshor 'khyams pa yis //
NK097(je)001:9798: mtha' yas pha ma mkha' mnyam sems can rnams //
NK097(je)001:9799: mthar 'dzin 'ching ba kun las rab grol nas //
NK097(je)001:9800: mtha' grol rdzogs pa chen po'i don rtogs shog /bdag la bzang ngan las kyis 'brel ba kun //
NK097(je)001:9801: myur lam zab mo 'di la rab brten te //
NK097(je)001:9802: mi rigs khyad chos drug gi gsang lam nas //
NK097(je)001:9803: kun bzang dgongs pa'i klong du grol bar shog /bdag kyang skye ba tshe rabs thams cad du //
NK097(je)001:9804: dga' rab dpa' bo'i rnam thar ji bzhin du //
NK097(je)001:9805: theg mchog rdzogs pa chen po'i bstan pa 'di //
NK097(je)001:9806: 'dzin skyong spel ba'i byed po nyid gyur cig /rgyal ba'i bstan pa spyi dang khyad par du //
NK097(je)001:9807: nang rgyud yo ga gsum gyi bstan pa 'di //
NK097(je)001:9808: mi nub phyogs dus kun tu rab rgyas nas //
NK097(je)001:9809: sa gsum dge legs snang bas khyab gyur cig /ris med bstan 'dzin dam pa'i tshogs rnams kyang //
NK097(je)001:9810: sku tshe mi 'gyur rdo rje'i khrir bzhugs nas //
NK097(je)001:9811: bstan 'gror sman pa'i rlabs chen mdzad pa yi //
NK097(je)001:9812: phrin las phyogs mthar rgyas pa'i rgyur gyur cig /mchog gsum bslu med gsum gyi bden stobs dang //
NK097(je)001:9813: rtsa gsum rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i byin rlabs dang //
NK097(je)001:9814: rgyud gsum rig 'dzin bla ma'i thugs rje'i mthus //
NK097(je)001:9815: smon pa'i gnas 'di gegs med 'grub gyur cig /
NK097(je)001:9816: 'od dkar snang bas tsha gdung sel ba ltar //
NK097(je)001:9817: lnga bdo'i rgud pa'i tsha gdung ma lus pa //
NK097(je)001:9818: cig char sel ba'i rdzogs ldan dpal yon gyi //
NK097(je)001:9819: bkra shis snang bas srid 'dir khyab gyur cig /rta bdun zer gyis mun pa sel ba ltar //
NK097(je)001:9820: rang byung rig pa'i nyin byed 'od stong gis //
NK097(je)001:9821: gnyis snang 'khrul ba'i mun pa drung phyung nas //
NK097(je)001:9822: 'ja' lus 'od skur grol ba'i bkra shis shog /ces
NK097(je)001:9823: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po'i rgyud kyi
NK097(je)001:9824: 'grel ba 'di nyid snga sor mkhan rin po che
NK097(je)001:9825: thub bstan pad+ma rab rgyas nas 'dren mchog 'khor lo'i
NK097(je)001:9826: mgon po mtshungs med thugs rje'i mnga' bdag drin chen
NK097(je)001:9827: theg mchog bstan 'dzin dang kho bo lhan du bkra
NK097(je)001:9828: shis pa'i lha reg dang bcas kun byed rgyal po'i
NK097(je)001:9829: rgyud sde 'di la 'grel pa zhig rtsom par gyis
NK097(je)001:9830: zhes nan tan chen po'i bskul ba la brten /
NK097(je)001:9831: kho bo lhan du rtsom gzhi tsam zhig byas nas yun ring lus par gyur pas /
NK097(je)001:9832: phyis skyabs rje 'gro ba'i mgon po nyid nas kyang
NK097(je)001:9833: rang res lhan du bri ba thog khel shin tu
NK097(je)001:9834: dka' bas khyod kyis kun byed 'grel pa de mthar
NK097(je)001:9835: phyin par gyis zhes gsung gnang byung ba zhal chem
NK097(je)001:9836: lta bur gyur nas dgongs pa dbyings su gshegs pa
NK097(je)001:9837: dang / mkhan chen bla ma nyid nas kyang da
NK097(je)001:9838: dung kho bo la nan bskul yang bskyar lan grangs
NK097(je)001:9840: bdag lta bu'i skyes sbyang gi shes rab dman par
NK097(je)001:9841: gyur cing zab mo'i don la blo kha tsam yang
NK097(je)001:9842: phyogs ma myong bas rgyud sde zab mo'i dgongs don
NK097(je)001:9843: 'grel ba'i nus pa med na yang /
NK097(je)001:9844: bshes gnyen dam pa zung gis bka' dang 'gal bar
NK097(je)001:9845: gyur na 'di phyi gnyis med du 'gyur ba'i tshul
NK097(je)001:9846: la skrag nas cung zad bri 'dun shar tshe /
NK097(je)001:9847: mkhyen mchog zur phud lnga pa'i sprul pa'i zlos gar
NK097(je)001:9848: chen po rigs dang dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i khyab bdag
NK097(je)001:9849: mtshan brjod par dka' ba 'jam mgon chos kyi blo
NK097(je)001:9850: gros kyi mdun nas de ltar brtsam par byas na
NK097(je)001:9851: bka' srung dregs pa'i tshogs kyis bka' chad sogs 'byung
NK097(je)001:9852: min gyi bka' 'dri dang rgyud 'di'i bka' gtad bcas
NK097(je)001:9853: zhus pas / bkra shis lha reg dang rin chen
NK097(je)001:9854: gnyis pa'i gnang sbyin dang bcas gsung gi dbug dbyung
NK097(je)001:9855: dang rgyud kyi bka' gtad mdzad pa la brten nas
NK097(je)001:9856: cung zad bri ba'i spobs pa skyes na yang /
NK097(je)001:9857: rang nyid 'khos stab zhan pas bri gzhi'i shog bu yang 'byor dka' ba dang /
NK097(je)001:9858: rang dgon gyi las khur cung zhig kyang thog tu bab pas lo shas su thogs par gyur kyang /
NK097(je)001:9859: phyis grogs mchog dam pa 'gas kyang de ltar grub na legs pa'i gsung gnang brtsal ba dang /
NK097(je)001:9860: rang yang dben pa'i gnas su cung zad sos dal
NK097(je)001:9861: thob pa sogs kyi mthun rkyen 'dzom pa la brten
NK097(je)001:9862: nas mnyam med thub pa'i dbang po'i rjes 'jug gi
NK097(je)001:9863: ming tsam 'dzin pa'i rmongs brtul snyoms las pa gzhan
NK097(je)001:9864: phan 'od zer du 'bod pas dben gnas 'chi med
NK097(je)001:9866: chu shel dbang po rgyu skar rgyal gyis nya ba'i
NK097(je)001:9867: zla ba rgyal sras in da b+ho d+his 'phur 'gro'i
NK097(je)001:9868: slob dpon chen po 'dzam gling gdul bya'i dpal du
NK097(je)001:9869: spyan drangs zhing / rgyal bur mnga' gsol bas rgyal
