NK097(je)001:9870: sras pad+ma rgyal po zhes pa'i mtshan snyan gyi ba
NK097(je)001:9871: dan dkar pos phyogs bcu'i zhing khams thams cad cig
NK097(je)001:9872: char du khyab par mdzad pa'i dus tshes bzang po'i
NK097(je)001:9873: phyogs la dpal gyi nyi ma shar ba'i 'grub sbyor
NK097(je)001:9874: dang bcas pa'i skabs su grub par bgyis pa 'adi'ang
NK097(je)001:9875: nges gsang snying po'i bstan pa phyogs dus gnas skabs
NK097(je)001:9876: kun tu dar zhing rgyas la yun ring du gnas
NK097(je)001:9881: ka dag spros bral gdod ma'i gzhi dbyings nas //
NK097(je)001:9882: rang gdangs lhun grub sna tshogs snang ba kun //
NK097(je)001:9883: rang snang nyid du mthong ste byang chub pa'i //
NK097(je)001:9884: thog ma'i mgon po kun tu bzang po nyid /
NK097(je)001:9885: 1 /khyad chos drug gi mngon par sangs rgyas shing //
NK097(je)001:9886: 'og min stug po bkod pa'i zhing khams su //
NK097(je)001:9887: longs spyod rdzogs sku'i ston par legs bzhengs te //
NK097(je)001:9888: 'khor tshogs ye shes rgya mtsho'i dkyil 'khor la /
NK097(je)001:9889: 2 /srid zhi gnyis med gdod nas sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK097(je)001:9890: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i chos kyi tshul //
NK097(je)001:9891: mi 'gyur dgongs pa rang byung ye shes mchog /ji bzhin nyid kyi gnas tshul rjen pa'i klong /
NK097(je)001:9892: 3 /ye shes gcig gi rtsal las ma g.yos par //
NK097(je)001:9893: dus gsum dus med dbyings na rtag tu 'doms //
NK097(je)001:9894: rang snang rnam dag 'og min chen po ru //
NK097(je)001:9895: dgongs rgyud zab mos bsnyad pa'i rdo rje'i chos /
NK097(je)001:9896: 4 /rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyud sde dpag med dag /me ri 'bar ba'i dur khrod chen po ru //
NK097(je)001:9897: rig kun 'dus pa'i khyab bdag rdo rje sems //
NK097(je)001:9898: rdzu 'phrul rol pa chen po'i gar bsgyur ba /
NK097(je)001:9899: 5 /sprul pa'i sku mchog dga' rab rdo rje la //
NK097(je)001:9900: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje yis //
NK097(je)001:9901: sdeb sbyor tshig la brten te rgyud rnams gsungs //
NK097(je)001:9902: de yis a ti'i rgyud sde mtha' dag kun /
NK097(je)001:9904: 6 / 'bum phrag drug cu'i bka' ru legs bsdus te //
NK097(je)001:9905: gnas mchog chen po so sa gling nyid du //
NK097(je)001:9906: 'jam dpal sprul pa many+dzu mi d+r+aa la //
NK097(je)001:9907: rang gnas nges pa'i sgo nas gdams par mdzad /
NK097(je)001:9908: 7 /de yi sde gsum man ngag so sor bkral //
NK097(je)001:9909: rgya nag ri bo do shar gnas mchog tu //
NK097(je)001:9910: rig 'dzin chen po sh+r+ai seng ha la //
NK097(je)001:9911: yid 'dzin blo bral gnyug ma'i ngang nas bshad /
NK097(je)001:9912: 8 /gang des phyi nang gsang ba yang gsang skor //
NK097(je)001:9913: man ngag dgongs don legs bkral phyi rabs kyi //
NK097(je)001:9914: bskal bzang tshogs la rgya gar b+ha seng ru //
NK097(je)001:9915: mchog thun brnyes pa dz+ny+aa na s+au tra la /
NK097(je)001:9916: 9 /rtogs pa mngon du gyur pa'i sgo nas gsungs //
NK097(je)001:9917: de yis dbus 'gyur 'od ma'i tshal gyi gnas //
NK097(je)001:9918: 'pho chen dngas ma'i sku brnyes bi ma lar //
NK097(je)001:9919: mngon sum rang gnas gtan la phabs te bshad /
NK097(je)001:9920: 10 /de tshe rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan gyi //
NK097(je)001:9921: pad+ma 'byung gnas bi ma mi tra sogs //
NK097(je)001:9922: b+ho ta'i gling 'dir snang ba'i rgyan du drangs //
NK097(je)001:9923: de'i tshe tshangs pa lha yi'i me tog dang /
NK097(je)001:9924: 11 /nyang ban sha yi spyan can la sogs pa //
NK097(je)001:9925: bskal bzang snod ldan slob ma'i tshogs rnams la //
NK097(je)001:9926: sde gsum klong dgu man ngag brgya phrag sogs //
NK097(je)001:9927: 'pho chen skur bzhengs slob dpon rnam gnyis kyi /
NK097(je)001:9928: 12 /brtse bas rjes bzung snod ldan tshogs la gdams //
NK097(je)001:9929: 'od gsal rdo rje snying po'i nyid byed dbang //
NK097(je)001:9930: gangs can skye 'gro kun gyi dpal du shar //
NK097(je)001:9931: des na mchog gsang rdzogs pa chen po'i don /
NK097(je)001:9932: 13 /kun bzang rdo rje 'chang chen nas bzung ste //
NK097(je)001:9933: da lta'i rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i tshogs rnams kun //
NK097(je)001:9934: grub pa'i sa brnyes zag phung 'od skur grub //
NK097(je)001:9935: chos rnams kun gyi yang zab 'di rmad byung /
NK097(je)001:9936: 14 /zab gsang man ngag snying po'i mthar thug don //
NK097(je)001:9937: 'khor 'das chos rnams kun gyi byed po mchog /
NK097(je)001:9938: 'bum phrag drug cu'i rgyud kyi rgyal po che'i //
NK097(je)001:9939: legs bshad 'od stong snang ba'i dkyil 'khor mdzes /
NK097(je)001:9941: 15 / 'jam dpal bshes gnyen ye shes sgyu ma'i 'phrul //
NK097(je)001:9942: skye dgu'i bsod nams dpyid du yongs shar ba //
NK097(je)001:9943: gzhan phan byang chub sems kyi rgyud brlan zhing //
NK097(je)001:9944: mkhyen brtse nus pa'i 'od zer stong 'bar ba /
NK097(je)001:9945: 16 /rmad byung las kyang rmad byung gsang ba'i mdzod //
NK097(je)001:9946: rgyud kyi rgyal po de nyid nges pa'i don //
NK097(je)001:9947: legs bshad nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor 'od stong 'bar //
NK097(je)001:9948: phun tshogs rmad byung bye ba'i 'byung gnas mchog 17 /grub dbang chos kyi nyi ma mgo tsh+wa zhes //
NK097(je)001:9949: thub bstan rab rgyas gling gi chos grwa che //
NK097(je)001:9950: glegs bam zad med gter gyi mdzod chen po //
NK097(je)001:9951: dge legs 'dod pa 'jo pa'i spar gyi 'phrul /
NK097(je)001:9952: 18 /don gnyer skye bo'i tshogs kun gsos su bzhengs //
NK097(je)001:9953: 'dis mtshon dus gsum bsags pa'i dge rtsa kun //
NK097(je)001:9954: rgyal ba'i bstan pa phyogs bcur rgyas pa dang //
NK097(je)001:9955: bstan 'dzin thugs bskyed bzhed don yid bzhin 'grub /
NK097(je)001:9956: 19 /dge 'dun sde rnams thugs mthun khrims gtsang zhing //
NK097(je)001:9957: bslab gsum bdud rtsi'i zas kyi bcud 'thung nas //
NK097(je)001:9958: mang thos sde snod mgrin pa'i rgyan 'chang ba'i //
NK097(je)001:9959: rgyal bstan dri med phyogs bcur rgyas gyur cig 20 /mtha' yas mkha' khyab srid pa'i 'gro ba kun //
NK097(je)001:9960: ma 'bad bzhin du gdod ma'i klong chen por //
NK097(je)001:9961: phyam gcig grol te nang dbyings bum pa'i skur //
NK097(je)001:9962: gdod ma'i klong du gtan srid zin par shog 21 /de ltar rang bzhin 'od gsal rdzogs pa che //
NK097(je)001:9963: thun min theg rtse gsang ba'i mdzod chen po'i //
NK097(je)001:9964: phyogs kyi tha gru kun tu khyab pa dang //
NK097(je)001:9965: srid mtha'i bar du dar smin rgyas gyur cig /ces
NK097(je)001:9966: pa 'adi'ang gsang chen nges pa'i rgyud kyi rgyal po
NK097(je)001:9967: chen po kun byed rgyal po'i legs bshad kun bzang
NK097(je)001:9968: dgongs rgyan 'di nyid spar du bskrun skabs su /
NK097(je)001:9969: lugs gnyis drin gyis bskyang ba'i mkhan rin po che
NK097(je)001:9970: o rgyan mgon dang dbon dam chos bsod nams gnyis
NK097(je)001:9971: kyi bka' yis bskul ngor ma ldog tsam du mgo
NK097(je)001:9972: tsh+wa sprul ming 'dzin pa pad+ma mdo sngags bstan 'dzin
